dn't%20refuse%20her%20and%20registered%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yediyurappa's%20office%20has%20rubbished%20the%20allegations%20as%20baseless%2C%20accusing%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter%20of%20filing%20over%2050%20complaints%20in%20the%20past.%20A%20list%20put%20out%20by%20Mr%20Yediyurappa's%20office%20showed%2053%20different%20complaints%20filed%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBS%20Yediyurappa%20served%20as%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202007%20and%20later%20from%202008%20to%202011.%20He%20was%20chief%20minister%20again%20for%20three%20days%20in%20May%202018%2C%20and%20then%20from%20July%202019%20to%20July%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710477840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fetivptd4_bs-yediyurappa-ndtv_625x300_26_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffir-against-bs-yediyurappa-for-alleged-sex-assault-of-17-year-old-girl-5241827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20over%20allegations%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20a%20teen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffir-against-bs-yediyurappa-for-alleged-sex-assault-of-17-year-old-girl-5241827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffir-against-bs-yediyurappa-for-alleged-sex-assault-of-17-year-old-girl-5241827%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffir-against-bs-yediyurappa-for-alleged-sex-assault-of-17-year-old-girl-5241827%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20's%20The%20Eras%20Tour%20to%20drop%20on%20OTT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710477776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1085