concerned%20and%20will%20closely%20monitor%20how%20India%20implements%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20on%20March%2011.%20We%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20this%20Act%20-%20how%20this%20Act%20will%20be%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Department%20Spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20told%20reporters%20at%20his%20daily%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRespect%20for%20religious%20freedom%20and%20equal%20treatment%20under%20the%20law%20for%20all%20communities%20are%20fundamental%20democratic%20principles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20implemented%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%202019%20on%20Monday%2C%20reducing%20the%20qualification%20period%20of%20application%20for%20citizenship%20from%2011%20to%205%20years%20for%20eligible%20migrants%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20came%20out%20with%20a%20press%20statement%20to%20say%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20need%20not%20worry%20as%20the%20CAA%20will%20not%20impact%20their%20citizenship%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20community%20which%20enjoys%20equal%20rights%20as%20their%20Hindu%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20about%20granting%20citizenship%20and%20that%20no%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20will%20lose%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710477300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F66me3qb8_mumbai-market_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconcerned-about-caa-will-closely-monitor-how-india-implements-it-us-5241828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20today%20said%20it%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20implemented%20by%20India%20to%20expedite%20the%20citizensh