20regulations.%20The%20lawsuit%20states%20that%20managers%20refused%20interpreters%20due%20to%20confidentiality%20concerns%2C%20despite%20established%20ethical%20codes%20for%20sign%20language%20interpreters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20accommodations%20left%20Ms%20Hall%20struggling%20to%20meet%20performance%20expectations.%20Unable%20to%20understand%20the%20video%20content%20efficiently%20without%20an%20interpreter%2C%20Ms%20Hall%20reportedly%20reviewed%20far%20fewer%20videos%20than%20the%20expected%20quota.%20This%20resulted%20in%20slow%20career%20progression%20compared%20to%20her%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20humiliated%2C%20realising%20that%20I%20would%20not%20grow%20in%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hall%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fgoogle-black-deaf-worker-diversity-suing-discrimination%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWired.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20details%20an%20instance%20where%20a%20manager%20referred%20to%20Ms%20Hall%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Baggressive%20black%20deaf%20woman%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20she%20take%20on%20a%20sales%20role%20instead.%20Additionally%2C%20Hall%20claims%20she%20was%20excluded%20from%20discussions%20and%20passed%20over%20for%20promotions%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20evaluations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Google%20has%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20procedural%20grounds%2C%20they%20haven't%20addressed%20the%20specific%20accusations.%20Ms%20Hall%2C%20however%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20see%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20is%20using%20me%20to%20make%20them%20look%20inclusive%20for%20the%20Deaf%20community%20and%20the%20overall%20disability%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hall%20told%20Wired.%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20they%20need%20to%20do%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hall's%20case%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20underrepresentation%20of%20black%20and%20disabled%20employees%20at%20Google%2C%20which%20is%20a%20company%20with%20nearly%20183%2C000%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlack%20women%2C%20specifically%2C%20have%20a%20higher%20departure%20rate%20than%20women%20of%20other%20races.%20Google's%20deaf%20and%20hard-of-hearing%20employee%20group%20reportedly%20consists%20of%20only%2040%20members%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.googleusercontent.com%2Fmedia%2Fabout.google%2Fen%2F%2Fbelonging%2Fdiversity-annual-report%2F2023%2Fstatic%2Fpdfs%2Fgoogle_2023_diversity_annual_report.pdf%3Fcachebust%3D2943cac%5C%22%3Ecompany%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hall's%20lawsuit%20seeks%20not%20only%20personal%20compensation%20but%20also%20systemic%20changes.%20She%20demands%20reinforcement%20policies%20to%20ensure%20future%20hires%20with%20disabilities%20receive%20proper%20accommodation%20and%20equal%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710476940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjc0a8ie_jalon-hall-_625x300_15_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjalon-hall-google-sued-by-black-employee-who-was-celebrated-as-diversity-success-5241989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Black%2C%20deaf%20Google%20employee%2C%20once%20celebrated%2C%20accuses%20discrimination%20based%20on%20disability%20and%20race%20despite%20the%20company's%20inclusive%20workplace%20image.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjalon-hall-google-sued-by-black-employee-who-was-celebrated-as-diversity-success-5241989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjalon-hall-google-sued-by-black-employee-who-was-celebrated-as-diversity-success-5241989%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjalon-hall-google-sued-by-black-employee-who-was-celebrated-as-diversity-success-5241989%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Future%20Gaming%2C%20Single-Biggest%20Electoral%20Bond%20Donor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Thursday%20uploaded%20data%20it%20has%20received%20from%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20on%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20which%20allowed%20individuals%20and%20companies%20to%20make%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20Coimbatore-based%20Future%20Gaming%20is%20the%20biggest%20donor%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20disclosed%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F17165220%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20donated%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20political%20parties%20between%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20January%2024%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201991%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20was%20earlier%20known%20as%20Martin%20Lottery%20Agencies%20Limited.%20It%20is%20owned%20by%20Santiago%20Martin%2C%20known%20as%20the%20'Lottery%20King'%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20firm's%20website%2C%20Mr%20Martin%20started%20out%20in%20the%20lottery%20business%20at%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20when%20%26quot%3Bhe%20had%20managed%20to%20develop%20and%20secure%20a%20vast%20marketing%20network%20of%20the%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20of%20lotteries%20all%20over%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20Gaming%20was%20the%20first%20lottery%20company%20in%20India%20to%20facilitate%20the%20live%20telecast%20on%20TV%20of%20the%20draws%20conducted%20by%20various%20governments%20for%20lotteries%20distributed%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%