ina.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710472821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15084758%2FGIo5duyWMAALYtP.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-will-visit-bhutan-next-week-neighbouring-pm-says-while-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bhutanese%20prime%20minister%20arrived%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20on%20his%20first%20overseas%20trip%20following%20his%20election%20victory%20in%20January.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-will-visit-bhutan-next-week-neighbouring-pm-says-while-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLike%20An%20Airplane%20On%20A%20Runway%26quot%3B%3A%20R%20Ashwin's%20Brutal%20Assessment%20Of%20Bazball%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20concluded%20Test%20series%20between%20India%20and%20England%20was%20a%20tough%20test%20for%20the%20Bazball%20style%20of%20cricket%20made%20famous%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20under%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Brendon%20McCullum%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F290-brendon-mccullum-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrendon%20McCullum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20visitors%20won%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Hyderabad%20but%20were%20completely%20outplayed%20in%20the%20next%20four%20games%20as%20they%20slumped%20to%20their%20first%20series%20defeat%20in%20the%20'Bazball'%20era.%20Veteran%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointed%20out%20a%20major%20flaw%20in%20Bazball%20as%20he%20explained%20in%20his%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQWVzLc7LUNg%5C%22%3EYouTube%20video%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20no%20form%20of%20cricket%20can%20be%20played%20in%20a%20similar%20pattern%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20adaptability%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20biggest%20problem%20for%20the%20England%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTest%20cricket%2C%20or%20any%20other%20form%20of%20cricket%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20cannot%20be%20played%20like%20an%20airplane%20on%20a%20runway.%20We%20cannot%20step%20on%20the%20pedal%20and%20accelerate%20till%20we%20take%20off!%20It's%20the%20same%20as%20driving%20on%20highways.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20I%20think%20of%20it%2C%20is%20it%20because%20of%20how%20they%20drive%20in%20England%3F%20Driving%20in%20England%20is%20bliss.%20No%20one%20comes%20in%20between.%20You%20can%20keep%20driving%20in%20the%20same%20lane.%20We%20cannot%20overtake%20on%20the%20left.%20They%20never%20expect%20unexpected%20things.%20If%20they%20see%20something%20unexpected%2C%20they%20crash.%20I%20have%20a%20feeling%20they%20will%20be%20very%20confused%20if%20they%20see%20how%20we%20drive%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%20you%20cannot%20always%20drive%20in%20the%20fourth%20gear.%20We%20keep%20changing%20gears.%20We%20always%20keep%20one%20foot%20on%20the%20brake.%20This%20concept%20is%20alien%20to%20them!%20Crawley%20always%20gets%20momentum%2C%20but%20cannot%20keep%20it%20going.%20Bazball%20is%20about%20the%20transfer%20of%20pressure%20onto%20the%20opponents.%20But%20after%20the%20transfer%20of%20pressure%2C%20what%20happens%3F%20They%20should%20be%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98we%20have%20to%20make%20them%20pay!'%20If%20they%20manage%20to%20do%20that%2C%20then%20the%20game%20is%20on.%20This%20series%20would%20have%20gone%20their%20way%20with%20the%20inexperience%20we%20had%20(in%20our%20ranks).%20They%20had%20a%20huge%20chance.%20Even%20before%20they%20came%20here%2C%20they%20were%20down%200-2%20in%20the%20Ashes%20and%20levelled%20it%20at%202-2.%20They%20then%20plundered%20Pakistan%20at%20their%20home.%20But%20this%20series%20loss%20is%20something%20that%20Ben%20Stokes%20and%20Co%20could%20learn%20from%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0a%20nine-wicket%20haul%20in%20his%20100th%20Test%20match%20helped%20Indian%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%C2%A0Ashwin%C2%A0re-claim%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%20bowlers'%20list%20of%20the%20latest%20ICC%20rankings%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%C2%A0was%20at%20his%20best%20throughout%20the%20Dharamsala%20contest%20against%20England%20as%20the%20experienced%20right-armer%20picked%20up%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20and%20then%20a%2036th%20five-wicket%20haul%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20as%20India%20cruised%20to%20a%20dominant%20triumph%20in%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20of%20their%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20haul%20helped%C2%A0Ashwin%C2%A0move%20past%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20premier%20position%20that%20he%20previously%20held%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710472620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9pmru7r8_ss_625x300_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Flike-an-airplane-on-a-runway-r-ashwins-brutal-assessment-of-englands-bazball-5237742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20delivered%20a%20huge%20verdict%20on%20Bazball%20after%20India's%20win%20over%20England%20in%20the%20Test%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle