2%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%3A%20Three%20Misgivings%20About%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Judgment%20That%20Need%20to%20Be%20Addressed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F09172044%2FScreen-Shot-2021-03-09-at-5.20.25-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20protracted%20legal%20battle%2C%20the%20information%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20finally%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20On%20March%2012%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sc-dismisses-sbis-plea-for-extension-says-disclose-information-by-march-12%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20to%20evade%20its%20directions%20to%20disclose%2C%20within%20three%20weeks%2C%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20transacted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDismissing%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20application%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%5C%22%3Eseeking%20four%20additional%20months%20to%20provide%20the%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India-led%20bench%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20one%20day%20for%20the%20SBI%20to%20furnish%20details%20of%20the%20donors%20and%20recipients%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI).%20The%20ECI%20was%20directed%20to%20upload%20this%20to%20their%20website%20by%20March%2015.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20important%20questions%20regarding%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Eseminal%20judgement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20warrant%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20is%20out.%20What%20next%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20judgement%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20disclosure%20of%20two%20sets%20of%20information%20since%20April%2012%2C%202019%3A%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20date%20of%20purchase%20of%20each%20Electoral%20Bond%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20purchased%E2%80%9D%3B%20and%20details%20of%20bonds%20redeemed%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20time%20frame%20to%20provide%20the%20information%2C%20the%20court%20clarified%20that%20it%20had%20never%20asked%20for%20information%20on%20purchasers%20and%20recipients%20to%20be%20decoded%20and%20matched.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20concern%20voiced%20by%20many%20is%20that%20shorn%20of%20details%20about%20who%20donated%20how%20much%20money%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20which%20party%2C%20the%20disclosures%20are%20of%20little%20value.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20a%20fully%20matched%20database%20of%20the%20purchasers%20and%20redeemers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20would%20have%20been%20ideal%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20information%20revealed%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20elections%20will%20greatly%20further%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know.%20Now%20that%20the%20data%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20those%20in%20pursuit%20of%20greater%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20political%20system%20will%20be%20empowered%20to%20examine%20the%20list%20of%20purchasers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20discern%20if%20they%20benefited%20from%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsFFkcewRp18%3Fsi%3DC__1-G1oZQdsrp9F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDid%20their%20loans%20get%20written%20off%3F%20Did%20they%20get%20a%20disproportionate%20share%20of%20government%20contracts%3F%20Did%20investigative%20agencies%20go%20slow%20on%20cases%20against%20them%20after%20they%20made%20donations%3F%20Were%20policy%20changes%20made%20to%20favour%20them%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20apart%20from%20tracing%20out%20shell%20companies%20or%20fly-by-night%20operators%2C%20perusing%20the%20financial%20statements%20of%20donor%20companies%20will%20reveal%20if%20loss-making%20entities%20donated%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20had%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20more%20plausible%20that%20loss-making%20companies%20will%20contribute%20to%20political%20parties%20with%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20the%20data%20will%20shine%20light%20on%20which%20foreign%20companies%20used%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20route%20to%20donate%20money%20anonymously%20through%20their%20Indian%20subsidiaries%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dogged%20fight%20put%20up%20by%20the%20government%20at%20every%20step%20to%20deny%20and%20delay%20disclosure%20reaffirms%20the%20old%20adage%20%E2%80%93%20information%20is%20power.%20It%20is%20now%20for%20people%20to%20engage%20with%20this%20crucial%20data%20and%20cast%20an%20informed%20vote%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20unaccounted%20cash%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judgement%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20not%20considering%20the%20effect%20that%20striking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20will%20have%20on%20political%20funding.%20No%20less%20than%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20vice-president%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPandaJay%2Fstatus%2F1758100836234719545%5C%22%3EBaijayant%20Jay%20Panda%2C%20tweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20infinitely%20better%20than%20what%20they%20had%20replaced%3A%20suitcases%20of%20illicit%20cash%E2%80%9D%2C%20claiming%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20perfect%20has%20become%20the%20enemy%20of%20the%20good%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20also%20a%20key%20argument%20of%20the%20government%20while%20defending%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20court%20%E2%80%93%20that%20bonds%20could%20only%20be%20purchased%20through%20banking%20channels%2C%20thereby%20curbing%20the%20use%20of%20black%20money%20for%20funding%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anonymity%20guaranteed%20to%20donors%20was%20meant%20to%20incentivise%20them%20to%20move%20away%20from%20cash%20donations%2C%20which%20they%20preferred%20because%20of%20fear%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconsequences%20from%20political%20opponents%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22After%20FAQs%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%20SBI's%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20Proformas%20Disappear%20from%20Website%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-faqs-on-electoral-bonds-sbis-beneficial-ownership-proformas-disappear-from-website%5C%22%3EAfter%20FAQs%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20Proformas%20Disappear%20from%20Website%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20dealt%20with%20this%20issue%20at%20length%20in%20its%20judgement%20under%20the%20heading%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20the%20infringement%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20is%20justified%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20noted%20that%20though%20the%20purported%20objective%20of%20guaranteeing%20the%20anonymity%20of%20donors%20was%20curbing%20black%20money%20by%20incentivising%20contributions%20through%20banking%20channels%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20regulatory%20check%20to%20prevent%20the%20trading%20of%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20concern%20had%20also%20been%20flagged%20by%20the%20RBI%20in%20its%20correspondence%20with%20the%20finance%20ministry%20while%20objecting%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELetters%20accessed%20by%20the%20authors%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20showed%20that%20the%20RBI%20warned%20the%20scheme%20could%20give%20rise%20to%20black%20money%20being%20laundered%2C%20as%20the%20bonds%20may%20be%20traded%20for%20a%20consideration%20without%20any%20trail%20of%20the%20transactions%20and%20the%20original%20buyer%20may%20not%20be%20the%20ultimate%20contributor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20and%20the%20concomitant%20amendments%20made%20to%20laws%20did%20not%20prohibit%20political%20parties%20from%20accepting%20donations%20in%20cash%3B%20instead%2C%20they%20just%20put%20a%20cap%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20on%20cash%20donations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20problems%20associated%20with%20anonymous%20donations%20in%20cash%20persisted%2C%20including%20the%20practice%20of%20breaking%20up%20large%20cash%20donations%20into%20smaller%20packets%20to%20hoodwink%20the%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20arrived%20at%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20failed%20the%20proportionality%20test.%20It%20ruled%20that%20though%20the%20scheme%20may%20reduce%20donations%20through%20cash%2C%20there%20are%20other%20alternative%20means%20through%20which%20the%20circulation%20of%20black%20money%20in%20electoral%20financing%20could%20be%20curbed%20that%20would%20not%20compromise%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSocJAoiGYto%3Fsi%3DdFaCgcKge2iUf325%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnwarranted%20breach%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20anonymity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20concern%20that%20has%20been%20flagged%20is%20that%20revealing%20the%20names%20of%20the%20purchasers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20that%20too%20with%20retrospective%20effect%2C%20is%20violative%20of%20the%20guarantee%20of%20anonymity%20made%20to%20the%20donors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20misplaced%20on%20at%20least%20two%20counts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20in%20clause%207(4)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20very%20clause%20which%20obligated%20the%20SBI%20to%20treat%20all%20information%20furnished%20by%20a%20buyer%20as%20confidential%20%E2%80%93%20defined%20the%20conditions%20under%20which%20details%20would%20be%20disclosed%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20demanded%20by%20a%20competent%20court%20or%20upon%20registration%20of%20criminal%20case%20by%20any%20law%20enforcement%20agency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20purchasers%20would%20have%20been%20aware%20at%20the%20time%20of%20buying%20a%20bond%20that%20there%20was%20no%20promise%20of%20blanket%20confidentiality.%20Since%2094%25%20of%20bonds%20sold%20in%20value%20terms%20were%20of%20the%20highest%20available%20denomination%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20fathom%20that%20these%20entities%2C%20presumably%20mostly%20corporates%2C%20would%20not%20have%20understood%20the%20applicable%20terms%20and%20conditions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20it%20is%20well%20within%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20while%20examining%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20a%20policy%20formulated%20by%20a%20government%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20it%20unreasonably%20abrogates%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information%2C%20to%20order%20the%20disclosure%20of%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20amendments%20made%20to%20various%20laws%20through%20the%20Finance%20Act%20of%202017%20to%20enable%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20including%20the%20aspect%20of%20purchasers%E2%80%99%20anonymity%2C%20were%20challenged%20in%202017%20even%20before%20the%20scheme%20was%20operationalised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20the%20court%20striking%20down%20the%20anonymity%20clause%20always%20existed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanjali-bhardwaj-and-amrita-johri%5C%22%3EAnjali%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Amrita%20Johri%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20transparency%20activists%20associated%20with%20the%20National%20Campaign%20for%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Right%20to%20Information%20and%20Satark%20Nagrik%20Sangathan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710472227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F09172044%2FScreen-Shot-2021-03-09-at-5.20.25-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fclearing-the-air-on-three-misgivings-around-the-electoral-bonds-judgement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20dogged%20fight%20put%20up%20by%20the%20government%20at%20every%20step%20to%20deny%20and%20delay%20disclosure%20reaffirms%20the%20old%20adage%20%E2%80%93%20information%20is%20power.%20It%20is%20now%20for%20people%20to%20engage%20with%20this%20crucial%20data%20and%20cast%20an%20informed%20vote%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fclearing-the-air-on-three-misgivings-around-the-electoral-bonds-judgement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Voting%20Was%20Held%20In%20Kerala%20For%20Russian%20Presidential%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20citizens%20residing%20in%20Kerala%20cast%20their%20votes%20for%20the%20Russian%20presidential%20elections%20at%20the%20booth%20specifically%20arranged%20at%20the%20Honorary%20Consulate%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20Russian%20House%2C%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatheesh%20Nair%2C%20Honorary%20Consul%20of%20Russia%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Russian%20House%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20said%2C%20that%20they%20arranged%20polling%20for%20the%20Russian%20presidential%20elections%20for%20the%20third%20time.%20He%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20Russian%20citizens%20in%20Kerala%20for%20their%20cooperation%20in%20the%20polling%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Ratheesh%20Nair%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20third%20time%20the%20Consulate%20of%20Russian%20Federation%20is%20hosting%20polling%20for%20the%20Russian%20presidential%20elections.%20This%20is%20actually%20for%20Russian%20nationalists%20staying%20here%20and%20also%20for%20the%20tourists.%20We%20are%20happy%20to%20associate%20with%20the%20Central%20Election%20Commission%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation.%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20Russian%20citizens%20in%20Kerala%20for%20their%20cooperation%20and%20enthusiasm%20to%20cast%20votes%20in%20the%20process%20of%20electing%20their%20new%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESergey%20Azurov%2C%20Senior%20Consul%20General%20in%20Chennai%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20organizing%20preliminary%20voting%20in%20the%20framework%20of%20presidential%20elections.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20citizens%20of%20Russian%20federations%20living%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUlia%2C%20a%20Russian%20citizen%2C%20said%20fellow%20natives%20in%20Kerala%20are%20thankful%20to%20the%20Russian%20house%20and%20consulate%20general%20in%20India%20for%20providing%20them%20the%20opportunity%20to%20cast%20votes%20in%20the%20Presidential%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Ulia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20who%20came%20today%20is%20Russian%20citizens%20either%20residing%20permanently%20in%20India%20or%20are%20visiting%20tourists.%20Everybody%20is%20thankful%20and%20happy%20to%20come%20here%20and%20participate%20in%20the%20election%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20for%20every%20citizen.%20This%20is%20our%20responsibility.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20thankful%20to%20the%20Russian%20house%20and%20the%20consulate%20general%20in%20India%20from%20Chennai%20for%20providing%20this%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20all%20set%20to%20hold%20presidential%20elections%20from%20March%2015-17.%20Russian%20citizens%20will%20vote%20from%20Friday%20until%20Sunday%20across%20the%2011%20time%20zones%20of%20the%20country.%20Russia's%20Central%20Election%20Commission%20(CEC)%20approved%20only%20three%20candidates%20to%20oppose%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20candidates%20standing%20against%20Putin%20are%20Leonid%20Slutsky%20of%20the%20Liberal%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20Vladislav%20Davankov%20of%20the%20New%20People%20Party%20and%20Nikolay%20Kharitonov%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party.%20All%20three%20men%20are%20thought%20to%20be%20satisfactorily%20pro-Kremlin%20and%20none%20is%20against%20Russia's%20military%20action%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20majority%20of%20opposition%20candidates%20are%20either%20dead%2C%20jailed%2C%20exiled%2C%20barred%20from%20running%20or%20simply%20token%20figures%2C%20a%20victory%20for%20Putin%20is%20all%20but%20guaranteed%2C%20according%20to%20a%20CNN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin's%20reelection%20would%20extend%20his%20rule%20until%20at%20least%202030.%20Following%20constitutional%20changes%20in%202020%2C%20he%20would%20then%20be%20able%20to%20run%20again%20and%20potentially%20stay%20in%20power%20until%202036.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710472200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fad2e0plo_russia-election_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvoting-held-in-kerala-for-russian-presidential-elections-5241038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian%20citizens%20residing%20in%20Kerala%20cast%20their%20votes%20for%20the%20Russian%20presidential%20elections%20at%20the%20booth%20specifically%20arranged%20at%20the%20Honorary%20Consulate%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20Russian%20House%2C%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvoting-held-in-kerala-for-russian-presidential-elections-5241038%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvoting-held-in-kerala-for-russian-presidential-elections-5241038%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvoting-held-in-kerala-for-russian-presidential-elections-5241038%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sid%20gets%20standing%20ovation%20at%20Yodha%20premiere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710472184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108508920%2Cimgsize-66156.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyodha-premiere-sidharth-malhotra-gets-a-standing-ovation-from-audience-watch%2Farticleshow%2F108508