s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-approves-first-drug-for-severe-form-of-fatty-liver-disease%2Famp_articleshow%2F108509008.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hackers-for-Hire%2C%20Govt's%20Media%20Control%3A%20Seven%20Takeaways%20From%20Studying%20the%20Arrests%20of%20the%20BK-16%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F21200002%2FScreen-Shot-2021-04-21-at-7.59.46-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20Alpa%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Incarcerations%3A%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20and%20the%20Search%20for%20Democracy%20in%20India%3Cem%3E%2C%20HarperCollins%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20sixteen%20largely%20unconnected%20people%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Delhi%20in%20the%20north%20to%20Hyderabad%20in%20the%20south%20%E2%80%93%20found%20themselves%20thrown%20into%20jail%20between%202018%E2%80%93%202020%2C%20accused%20of%20being%20Maoist%20terrorists%2C%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99.%20As%20this%20book%20has%20shown%2C%20they%20were%20all%20%E2%80%98custodians%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20people%20who%20had%20persistently%20supported%20grassroots%20social%20movements%20against%20rising%20inequality%2C%20land%20grabs%20and%20state%20atrocities%2C%20and%20protecting%20environmental%2C%20land%20and%20forest%20rights.%20They%20had%20fought%20for%20the%20social%20justice%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20vulnerable%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20and%20they%20had%20done%20so%20no%20matter%20what%20regime%20was%20in%20power.%20While%20some%20of%20them%20knew%20each%20other%20and%20had%20worked%20together%2C%20many%20found%20themselves%20standing%20in%20solidarity%20with%20one%20another%20only%20after%20the%20Pune%20City%20Police%20tied%20them%20together%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20case%20as%20the%20BK-16.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20years%20of%20digging%20deep%20into%20the%20BK%20case%2C%20a%20few%20things%20are%20clear.%20The%20first%20is%20that%20this%20was%20a%20targeted%20state-driven%20attempt%20to%20silence%20the%20BK-16.%20Exactly%20when%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20state%20got%20involved%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20know.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20the%20case%20was%20moved%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20central%20anti-terror%20task%20force%2C%20the%20NIA%2C%20in%202020%2C%20it%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20government.%20How%20and%20why%20particular%20individuals%20within%20the%20state%20acted%20as%20they%20did%20is%20also%20hard%20to%20know.%20But%20my%20interview%20with%20one%20of%20the%20police%20officers%20closely%20involved%20in%20the%20first%20two%20rounds%20of%20arrests%2C%20Shivaji%20Bodkhe%2C%20revealed%20that%20at%20least%20some%20of%20them%20were%20driven%20by%20a%20moral%20conviction%20that%20they%20were%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20for%20the%20public%20good.%20Bodkhe%20was%20certain%20that%20the%20BK-16%20were%20left-wing%20extremists%20responsible%20for%20violence%20and%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20that%20their%20incarcerations%20was%20a%20high%20point%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20376px)%2085vw%2C%20376px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15081034%2FThe-Incarcerations_India-Cover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15081034%2FThe-Incarcerations_India-Cover.jpg%20797w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15081034%2FThe-Incarcerations_India-Cover-199x300.jpg%20199w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15081034%2FThe-Incarcerations_India-Cover-680x1024.jpg%20680w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701744%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAlpa%20Shah%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Incarcerations%3A%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20and%20the%20Search%20for%20Democracy%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20thing%20that%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20evidence%20used%20to%20turn%20the%20public%20against%20the%20BK-16%2C%20incriminate%20and%20incarcerate%20them%2C%20was%20fabricated%20and%20planted%20on%20some%20of%20their%20computers.%20Such%20is%20the%20extent%20of%20evidence%20tampering%2C%20that%20the%20BK%20case%20has%20become%20a%20landmark%20for%20research%20into%20cyber%20espionage%2C%20attracting%20those%20at%20its%20global%20frontiers.%20Cyber%20warfare%20is%20a%20field%20about%20which%20many%20of%20us%20know%20little%2C%20yet%20is%20now%20considered%20the%20fifth%20domain%20of%20warfare%20%E2%80%93%20alongside%20the%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20air%20and%20space%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20as%20this%20book%20shows%2C%20it%20will%20need%20to%20be%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20future%20global%20concerns%20for%20protecting%20democratic%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-based%20experts%20who%20took%20an%20interest%20in%20the%20cyber-data%20of%20the%20BK%20case%20have%20shown%20that%20there%20is%20a%20link%20between%20the%20police%20who%20made%20the%20arrests%20and%20those%20who%20hacked%20the%20computers.%20Part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20they%20have%20been%20able%20to%20trace%20these%20links%20and%20unveil%20the%20extent%20of%20hacking%2C%20snooping%2C%20and%20evidence%20tampering%2C%20is%20because%20it%20was%20a%20shoddy%20job.%20Indeed%2C%20so%20poorly%20fabricated%20was%20some%20of%20the%20evidence%20that%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20most%20incriminating%20parts%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20the%20letter%20used%20by%20the%20police%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20BK-16%20were%20plotting%20to%20assassinate%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20actually%20appear%20in%20the%20draft%20charges%20filed%20by%20the%20NIA%20against%20those%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cyber%20espionage%20research%20also%20leads%20to%20a%20third%20revelation.%20This%20is%20that%20the%20evidence%20used%20to%20incarcerate%20the%20BK-16%20was%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20implanted%20remotely%20through%20a%20hacker-for-hire%20mercenary%20gang%20infrastructure%20that%20has%20clients%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20but%20whose%20epicentre%20is%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20revelation%20is%20that%20the%20BK-16%20arrests%20were%20used%20to%20divert%20attention%20away%20from%20the%20Hindutva%20instigators%20of%20a%20communal%20riot%20targeting%20Dalits%20which%20took%20place%20on%201%20January%202018%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon.%20Hindutva%20leaders%20Milind%20Ekbote%20and%20Sambhaji%20Bhide%20were%20reported%20to%20be%20mobilising%20local%20Marathas%20against%20the%20Dalits%20and%20inciting%20communal%20tension%2C%20including%20in%20the%20days%20just%20before%20the%20violence.%20Although%20one%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20Milind%20Ekbote%20%E2%80%93%20was%20initially%20imprisoned%20by%20the%20Pune%20Rural%20Police%20for%20inciting%20the%20riots%2C%20within%20a%20month%20he%20was%20let%20out%20of%20jail.%20A%20whole%20new%20narrative%20of%20the%20violence%20emerged%20from%20the%20Pune%20City%20Police%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20conduct%20raids%20on%20some%20of%20the%20BK-16%20and%20allege%20that%20they%20had%20incited%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20violence%2C%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20incarceration%20of%20the%20BK-16.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20the%20BK%20case%20provides%20a%20window%20into%20how%20many%20state%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20judiciary%2C%20have%20come%20to%20be%20dominated.%20And%20how%20vigilante%20organisations%20across%20the%20country%20have%20nurtured%20militant%20youth%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20moral%20policing%20of%20society%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20mobs%20who%20attacked%20Dalits%20on%201%20January%202018.%20The%20police%20force%20appears%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20stand%20back%20and%20grant%20a%20long%20leash%20to%20offenders%2C%20even%20protect%20them%2C%20for%20instance%20by%20overlooking%20the%20alleged%20crimes%20of%20Milind%20Ekbote%20and%20Sambhaji%20Bhide%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20incarcerating%20those%20it%20wants%20to%20silence%2C%20like%20the%20BK-16.%20The%20regime%20also%20has%20at%20its%20disposal%20a%20set%20of%20draconian%20anti-terror%20laws%20like%20the%20UAPA%2C%20which%20allow%20it%20to%20put%20dissenters%20behind%20bars%20without%20any%20trial.%20Entire%20parts%20of%20the%20judiciary%20have%20largely%20buckled%20to%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20demands%20%E2%80%93%20as%20we%20see%20in%20the%20number%20of%20recusals%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20multiple%20bail%20rejections%2C%20and%20the%20refusal%20even%20to%20look%20at%20the%20Arsenal%20reports%2C%20which%20show%20that%20the%20main%20evidence%20used%20to%20incarcerate%20the%20BK-16%20was%20fabricated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelated%20to%20this%2C%20is%20a%20sixth%20revelation%20about%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20to%20dominate%20narratives%20and%20communications%20networks.%20Mainstream%20media%20is%20increasingly%20ready%20to%20propagate%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20events.%20This%20was%20clear%20in%20the%20media%20trials%20that%20dramatically%20flashed%20the%20fabricated%20Modi%20assassination%20plot%20letter%20across%20the%20country%20and%20declared%20the%20BK%20activists%20to%20be%20guilty%20before%20the%20matter%20even%20reached%20the%20courts.%20Those%20media%20outlets%20which%20challenged%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20events%20were%20targeted%20in%20order%20to%20be%20silenced%2C%20as%20is%20evident%20with%20the%20raids%20on%20independent%20news%20outlets%2C%20cases%20filed%20against%20journalists%2C%20and%20their%20arrest.%20Any%20critics%20of%20the%20government%20risk%20being%20labelled%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%20And%20anyone%20speaking%20out%20for%20or%20raising%20their%20voice%20in%20support%20of%20those%20already%20persecuted%2C%20like%20the%20BK-16%2C%20risk%20being%20targeted%20as%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20threat%20of%20incarceration%20under%20anti-terror%20laws.%20In%20fact%2C%20after%20the%20BK-16%20incarcerations%2C%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%20has%20become%20a%20common%20term%20to%20brand%20any%20form%20of%20dissent%20against%20the%20government%2C%20used%20by%20both%20the%20media%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Although%20a%20right%20to%20information%20query%20filed%20in%202020%20by%20India%20Today%20TV%20revealed%20that%20the%20Left%20Wing%20Extremism%20Division%20in%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20had%20no%20information%20on%20who%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99%20are%20and%20where%20they%20operate%2C%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%20is%20one%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20favoured%20terms%20to%20delegitimise%20any%20opposition%20including%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20what%20is%20also%20revealed%20through%20the%20BK%20case%20is%20how%20international%20economic%20and%20financial%20institutions%20can%20be%20complicit%20in%20not%20only%20propping%20up%20but%20also%20weaponising%20a%20regime%20that%20wants%20to%20target%20democratic%20rights%20activists.%20Events%20like%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20bringing%20together%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20significant%20economies%2C%20or%20the%20Summit%20for%20Democracy%20hosted%20by%20the%20US%20to%20renew%20democracy%20at%20home%20and%20confront%20autocracies%20abroad%2C%20give%20legitimacy%20to%20authoritarian%20leaders%20and%20regimes%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20RSS%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20allow%20them%20to%20co-opt%20and%20subvert%20the%20meaning%20of%20democracy.%20These%20are%20in%20some%20ways%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20welcome%2C%20and%20therefore%20legitimacy%2C%20that%20Modi%20has%20received%20from%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20governments%20once%20he%2