20Lenders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETech%20firm%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20Pvt%20must%20freeze%20%24533%20million%20to%20protect%20the%20money%20for%20disgruntled%20lenders%20who%20claim%20the%20cash%20should%20only%20be%20used%20to%20pay%20them%2C%20a%20US%20judge%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20by%20US%20Bankruptcy%20Judge%20John%20Dorsey%20was%20a%20mixed%20victory%20for%20lenders.%20They%20earlier%20demanded%20the%20money%20be%20placed%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20federal%20court%20to%20prevent%20the%20cash%20from%20being%20spent%20by%20the%20education-tech%20firm%2C%20which%20operates%20under%20the%20name%20Byju's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Dorsey's%20order%20was%20aimed%20at%20Riju%20Ravindran%2C%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20directors%20and%20the%20brother%20of%20founder%20Byju%20Raveendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindran%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20help%20solve%20one%20of%20the%20central%20mysteries%20of%20the%20court%20dispute%3A%20where%20the%20money%20is%20located.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20him%20when%20he%20says%20he%20cannot%26quot%3B%20learn%20the%20location%20from%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%2C%20Judge%20Dorsey%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20declined%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindran's%20attorney%2C%20Sheron%20Korpus%20argued%20that%20the%20lenders%20are%20at%20fault%20for%20any%20financial%20woes%20suffered%20by%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn.%20The%20company%20was%20justified%20in%20keeping%20the%20money%20away%20from%20the%20lenders%20because%20they%20had%20been%20overly%20aggressive%20in%20claiming%20the%20debt%20was%20in%20default%2C%20Korpus%20told%20the%20judge.%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20is%20fighting%20the%20lenders%20in%20state%20courts%20in%20Delaware%20and%20New%20York.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenders%20had%20previously%20seized%20control%20of%20a%20holding%20company%20set%20up%20by%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20to%20issue%20%241.2%20billion%20in%20debt.%20That%20unit%2C%20Byju's%20Alpha%2C%20is%20now%20in%20bankruptcy%20under%20Judge%20Dorsey's%20oversight.%20Ravindran%20is%20appealing%20a%20decision%20by%20Delaware's%20Chancery%20Court%20approving%20that%20seizure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Thursday%20bankruptcy%20hearing%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20Delaware%2C%20Judge%20Dorsey%20ordered%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20small%20Florida%20hedge%20fund%20for%20refusing%20to%20reveal%20where%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20allegedly%20hid%20the%20cash.%20If%20he%20can%20be%20located%20by%20US%20Marshals%2C%20William%20C%20Morton%20will%20be%20locked%20up%20for%20contempt%20of%20court%20under%20Judge%20Dorsey's%20order.%20Morton%20must%20also%20pay%20%2410%2C000%20a%20day%20until%20he%20provides%20details%20about%20the%20money%2C%20which%20was%20briefly%20placed%20with%20the%20hedge%20fund%20Camshaft%20Capital%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missing%20money%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20fight%20between%20lenders%20owed%20more%20than%20%241.2%20billion%20and%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn.%20The%20%24533%20million%20was%20transferred%20to%20Morton's%20hedge%20fund%20and%20then%20moved%20to%20an%20unnamed%2C%20off-shore%20trust%2C%20Byju's%20Alpha%20lawyer%20Benjamin%20Finestone%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20is%20in%20serious%20financial%20trouble%20and%20faces%20disputes%20with%20its%20shareholders%20and%20court%20fights%20with%20its%20lenders%2C%20Finestone%20said%20during%20the%20hearing.%20Ravindran%20also%20testified%20Thursday%20that%20three%20of%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn's%20six%20directors%20have%20resigned%2C%20leaving%20only%20himself%2C%20his%20brother%2C%20and%20his%20sister-in-law%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20substantively%20important%20that%20we%20get%20these%20funds%2C%20because%20the%20walls%20are%20crumbling%2C%26q