nessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-launch-rocket-blows-up-explosion-elon-musk-mars-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20explosions%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20critical%20to%20helping%20SpaceX%20hone%20the%20technology%20that%20led%20to%20Thursday's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20innovations%20that%20we've%20developed%20have%20come%20from%20our%20failures%2C%20and%20they%20teach%20us%20how%20to%20avoid%20the%20perils%20of%20spaceflight%2C%26quot%3B%20Siva%20Bharadvaj%2C%20space%20operations%20engineer%20at%20SpaceX%2C%20said%20during%20the%20launch%20live%20stream%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starship%2028%20lifting%20off%20from%20base%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f330953037f8e817507305%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarship%2028%20lifting%20off%20from%20Starbase%20in%20Boca%20Chica%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20second%20explosion%20in%20November%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20tasked%20SpaceX%20with%2017%20corrective%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20included%20hardware%20redesigns%2C%20engine%20analyses%2C%20and%20robustness%20updates%20to%20both%20its%20first-stage%20Super%20Heavy%20booster%20and%20upper-stage%20Starship%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tough%20business%2C%20but%20all%20of%20this%20testing%2C%20all%20of%20the%20iterative%20design%2C%20allows%20us%20to%20make%20the%20design%20better%20and%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20SpaceX%20rocket%20upgrades%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SpaceX's%20Starship%20spacecraft%20and%20Super%20Heavy%20rocket%20explodes%20after%20launch%20from%20Starbase%20on%20April%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f3806e857f90b71522ca7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpaceX's%20Starship%20spacecraft%20and%20Super%20Heavy%20rocket%20explodes%20after%20launch%20from%20Starbase%20on%20April%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Newton%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20seven%20minutes%20into%20November's%20test%20launch%2C%20Starship%20initiated%20a%20pre-planned%20dump%20of%20excess%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20triggering%20a%20fire%20that%20ultimately%20caused%20the%20ship%20to%20self-detonate%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspacenews.com%2Ffaa-closes-investigation-into-second-starship-test-flight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceNews.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20avoiding%20a%20similar%20fire%20was%20top%20of%20mind%20in%20preparation%20for%20Thursday's%20launch.%20SpaceX%20made%20several%20adjustments%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20SpaceX%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20a%20liquid%20oxygen%20dump%20before%20engine%20cutoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20company%20stated%20that%20Starship%20caught%20fire%20due%20to%20a%20leak%20that%20occurred%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20liquid%20oxygen%20dump.%20So%2C%20SpaceX%20made%20some%20hardware%20changes%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20leaks%2C%20per%20SpaceNews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20also%20equipped%20its%20newest%20Starship%20prototype%20with%20additional%20fire%20protection%20and%20performed%20flammability%20analysis%20updates%20to%20reduce%20fire%20risk%2C%20according%20to%20an%20FAA%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20effort%20paid%20off%20since%20there%20was%20no%20fire%20during%20Thursday's%20launch.%20But%20that%20was%20just%20some%20of%20the%20changes.%20SpaceX%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-starship-rocket-design-evolution-launch-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20several%20upgrades%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20improve%20engine%20and%20flight%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20SpaceX%20updated%20Super%20Heavy's%20engine%20control%20algorithms%20and%20added%20new%2C%20large%20slosh%20baffles%20to%20its%20liquid%20oxygen%20tank%20to%20reduce%20propellant%20from%20sloshing%20around%20too%20much%20during%20the%20booster's%20challenging%20flip%20maneuver%2C%20per%20SpaceNews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-spacex-starship-is-black-and-silver-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20for%20Starship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SpaceX%20added%20three%20new%20angled%20liquid%20oxygen%20vents%20to%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20engine%20skirt%20that%20likely%20helped%20with%20attitude%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20cowbell%20diverters%20the%20two%20large%20header%20tank%20vents%20on%20the%20spaceship's%20nose%20cone%20to%20direct%20the%20flow%20of%20vented%20vapors%20downward%2C%20also%20aided%20attitude%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starship%2028%20nose%20cone%20with%20circled%20cowbell%20diverters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f33397857f90b71522986d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20image%20of%20Starship%2028's%20nose%20cone%20shows%20the%20new%20cowbell%20diverters%20(circled%20in%20red)%20covering%20vents%20to%20direct%20the%20flow%20of%20vapors%20downward.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EStrengthened%20data%20connection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Starship%20blasted%20off%2C%20it%20sent%20stunning%20views%20of%20space%20back%20to%20Earth%2C%20maintaining%20a%20strong%20data%20connection%20to%20mission%20control%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20space%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarship%20even%20captured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-reentry-video-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estunning%20video%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20spacecraft's%20re-entry%20to%20Earth's%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starship%2028%20re-entering%20Earth's%20atmosphere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f32c8a857f90b7152292f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarship%2028%20sent%20back%20footage%20of%20plasma%20formation%20during%20the%20spaceship's%20re-entry%20to%20Earth's%20atmosphere.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20all%20thanks%20to%20upgrades%20to%20the%20rocket's%20Starlink%20terminals%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-starlink-satellites-internet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarlink%20satellite%3C%2Fa%3E%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMore%20improvements%20to%20come%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20we%20don't%20know%20when%20the%20next%20Starship%20mission%20will%20launch%2C%20the%20new%20iteration%20of%20this%20mega-rocket%20will%20likely%20come%20with%20even%20more%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20was%20the%20most%20successful%20Starship%20test%20launch%20to%20date%2C%20it%20didn't%20achieve%20all%20mission%20objectives.%20After%20separating%20from%20Starship%2C%20the%20Super%20Heavy%20booster%20lost%20control%20and%20began%20to%20tumble%20toward%20Earth.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20led%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-falcon-9-rocket-booster-crash-video-crs16-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20hard%20splashdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20gentle%2C%20splashdown%20like%20SpaceX%20had%20planned%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasaspaceflight.com%2F2024%2F03%2Fstarship-3rd-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASA%20Spaceflight%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Starship%20was%20lost%20during%20re-entry%20meaning%20SpaceX%20will%20have%20to%20perform%20a%20mishap%20investigation%20like%20its%20previous%2C%20November%20flight%20to%20determine%20what%20went%20wrong%2C%20per%20NASA%20Spaceflight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20mishaps%2C%20Starship's%20third%20test%20flight%20was%20a%20resounding%20success.%20SpaceX%20is%20used%20to%20unexpected%20fires%2C%20tumbles%2C%20and%20explosions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20not%20afraid%20of%20them%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20failing%2C%20you're%20not%20learning%20and%20improving%20the%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20SpaceX%20Quality%20Systems%20Engineer%2C%20Kate%20Tice%2C%20said%20during%20Thursday's%20live%20stream%20of%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20officials%20said%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20complete%20at%20least%20six%20more%20Starship%20test%20flights%20this%20year%2C%20subject%20to%20regulatory%20approval%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fspace%2Fspacex-hoping-launch-starship-farther-third-test-flight-2024-03-14%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-spacex-flew-starship-space-first-time-crucial-upgrades-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710466503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f3bf3b1851e792f0eff10c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-spacex-flew-starship-space-first-time-crucial-upgrades-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX%20finally%20flew%20its%20Starship%20mega-rocket%20to%20space%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20but%20it%20couldn't%20have%20done%20so%20without%20some%20crucial%20upgrades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellyn%20Lapointe)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-spacex-flew-starship-space-first-time-crucial-upgrades-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20MGNREGS%20Continues%20To%20Falter%20In%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBhagalpur%20and%20Vaishali%20(Bihar)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20In%20December%202023%2C%20almost%20800%20people%E2%80%93of%20whom%20700%20were%20women%E2%80%93participated%20in%20a%20strike%20of%20workers%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(MGNREGS)%20in%20the%20Patepur%20block%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Vaishali%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narega%20Sangarsh%20Morcha%2C%20a%20nationwide%20forum%20for%20workers%2C%20listed%20the%20issues%20in%20a%20social%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100069390431555%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0iuyFW88HjK5SQ576Fa4xLwj1e2Y176UzR4whoJ5SzVhWu2BSybDbyLn8rVofcAiHl%2F%3Fapp%3Dfbl%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epost%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20major%20issue%20being%20the%20alleged%20fraud%20within%20the%20MGNREGS%20scheme%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20scam%20involves%20adding%20labourers%E2%80%99%20names%20to%20the%20muster%20rolls%20without%20their%20knowledge%20and%20falsely%20marking%20their%20attendance%20on%20the%20National%20Mobile%20Monitoring%20System%20(NMMS)%20app%2C%20which%20records%20the%20daily%20attendance%20of%20workers%20on%20the%20site.%20Payments%20meant%20for%20these%20labourers%20were%20redirected%20to%20corrupt%20officials%2C%20including%20those%20at%20various%20levels%20of%20government%20from%20blocks%20to%20districts%2C%20the%20Jan%20Vikas%20Shakti%20Sangathan%20(JVSS)%20alleged.%20JVSS%20is%20an%20organisation%20for%20labourer-farmers%2C%20and%20for%20the%20exploited%20and%20deprived%2C%20and%20it%20fights%20for%20them%20primarily%20by%20creating%20awareness%20of%20their%20rights%20including%20rations%2C%20pensions%2C%20education%2C%20land%20issues%2C%20health%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patepur%20strikers%20demanded%20action%20against%20corrupt%20officials%2C%20an%20investigation%20into%20and%20cessation%20of%20these%20scams.%20Further%2C%20they%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20corruption%20in%20the%20MGNREGS%2C%20resolution%20of%20delayed%20wage%20payment%2C%20redressal%20of%20unavailability%20of%20work%2C%20and%20the%20resolving%20of%20issues%20concerning%20job%20cards%2C%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20by%20block%20officers%20etc.%20The%20protests%20lasted%20five%20days%20and%20ended%20on%20December%208%2C%20when%20they%20were%20assured%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fh-library%2Fjvss-letter.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edemands%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20looked%20into%2C%20JVSS%20activist%20Ranjan%20Kumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20November%202023%2C%20representatives%20from%2018%20states%20including%20Bihar%20and%20more%20than%2040%20labour%20unions%2Forganisations%20and%20activists%20working%20for%20improved%20MGNREGS%20implementation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNREGA_Sangharsh%2Fstatus%2F1708687733198143753%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etook%20part%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20National%20Convention%20of%20Nrega%20Sangharsh%20Morcha.%20They%20voiced%20their%20concerns%20about%20delayed%20payments%3B%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20MGNREGS%20earnings%20were%20less%20than%20the%20minimum%20wages%20set%20by%20the%20state%3B%20budget%20cuts%3B%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20and%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20technology%20interventions%20to%20deter%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20introduced%20various%20public%20works-based%20employment%20programmes%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20rural%20poor%2C%20mostly%20agricultural%20labourers%20who%20rely%20on%20daily%20labour%20wages.%20However%2C%20the%20programmes%20did%20not%20adequately%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20rural%20employment.%20To%20tackle%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%20introduced%20the%20MGNREGS%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsimdega.nic.in%2Fen%2Fscheme%2Fmahatma-gandhi-national-rural-employment-guarantee-act-mgnrega%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2006%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20programme%20is%20variously%20referred%20to%20as%20MGNREGA%20(the%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%20standing%20for%20the%20Act%20passed%20to%20codify%20the%20programme)%2C%20MNREGA%20and%20NREGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20aimed%20to%20provide%20at%20least%20100%20days%20of%20guaranteed-wage%20employment%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20willing%20to%20engage%20in%20unskilled%20manual%20work%20during%20each%20financial%20year.%20The%20MGNREGS%20differs%20from%20earlier%20wage%20employment%20programmes%20as%20it%20involves%20a%20rights-based%20approach%2C%20where%20the%20government%20is%20obligated%20to%20provide%20work%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20request.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20entitles%20workers%20to%20unemployment%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20employment%20opportunities%20should%20ideally%20be%20available%20within%20a%20distance%20of%205%20km%20from%20the%20job-seeker%E2%80%99s%20village.%20If%20work%20is%20offered%20beyond%20this%20limit%2C%20an%20additional%20payment%20of%2010%25%20is%20required%20to%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20transportation%20and%20accommodation.%20Availability%20of%20shade%2C%20adequate%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20first%20aid%20are%20musts%20at%20every%20work%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20law%20is%20especially%20significant%20for%20female%20workers%20because%20it%20reserves%20a%20minimum%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1942781%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone-third%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20total%20workdays%20for%20them%3B%20it%20provides%20opportunities%20for%20unskilled%20manual%20labour%3B%20it%20requires%20that%20work%20be%20done%20locally%3B%20and%20it%20stipulates%20that%20in%20the%20event%20there%20are%20more%20than%20five%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20six%20at%20a%20given%20worksite%2C%20on-site%20child%20care%20must%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20programme%20officer%20must%20be%20notified%20by%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20prior%20to%20beginning%20any%20work%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%20system.%20The%20officer%20then%20issues%20the%20necessary%20muster%20rolls%3B%20each%20roll%20requires%20a%20unique%20identity%20number%20and%20must%20be%20certified%20to%20all%20executing%20agencies%2C%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20and%20the%20programme%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20job%20card%20number%2C%20name%2C%20and%20number%20of%20days%20worked%20are%20listed%20on%20the%20muster%20roll.%20Together%20with%20each%20worker%E2%80%99s%20signature%20or%20thumb%20impression%2C%20the%20attendance%20of%20the%20workers%20and%20the%20pay%20received%20will%20be%20displayed%20against%20their%20names.%20If%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20name%20appears%20in%20the%20muster%20roll%2C%20he%20or%20she%20should%20be%20able%20to%20access%20that%20information%20in%20order%20to%20know%20the%20worksite%20details%2C%20nature%20of%20work%2C%20and%20number%20of%20allotted%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EToo%20many%20people%2C%20too%20little%20work%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThirty-nine-year-old%20Shiv%20Kumari%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Manjhi%20community%2C%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Nilo%20Rukunpur%20panchayat%20in%20Vaishali%20district%20and%20was%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20the%20Patepur%20strike.%20The%20Manjhi%20community%20were%20traditionally%20engaged%20in%20boating%20and%20fishing.%20Very%20few%20Manjhi%20own%20their%20own%20land%3B%20thus%2C%20most%20of%20them%20work%20as%20labourers%20on%20others%E2%80%99%20property.%20In%202023%2C%20Kumari%20got%20a%20total%20of%2015%20days%20of%20work%2C%20and%20she%20is%20yet%20to%20receive%20pay%20for%2010%20days.%20Her%20husband%20is%20a%20migrant%20worker%20living%20in%20Kolkata.%20%E2%80%9CThe%2010%20days%20of%20work%20that%20I%20got%20is%20economically%20valuable%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20six%20kathas%20(one%20acre%20equals%2032%20kathas)%20of%20land%2C%20and%20I%20have%20two%20children%20aged%2015%20and%2018.%20The%20land%20is%20too%20little%20to%20provide%20for%20our%20needs.%20There%20is%20no%20other%20work%20except%20MNREGA%20work%20that%20is%20available%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%20If%20she%20would%20have%20secured%20the%20promised%20100%20days%E2%80%99%20work%2C%20her%20household%20situation%20would%20have%20been%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPramila%20Devi%2C%20aged%2043%2C%20was%20also%20among%20those%20who%20protested%20at%20Patepur.%20She%20complained%20of%20getting%20only%2020%20days%20of%20work.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20received%20payment%20for%20only%2011%20days%20of%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20my%20name%20was%20there%20in%20the%20issued%20muster%20roll%20but%20I%20was%20informed%20about%20work%20only%20four%20days%20later.%E2%80%9D%20Pramila%20Devi%20too%20belongs%20to%20the%20Manjhi%20community%2C%20and%20her%20family%20owns%20no%20land.%20Due%20to%20lack%20of%20money%2C%20her%20children%20could%20not%20continue%20their%20education.%20Her%20sons%2C%20aged%2017%20and%2021%2C%20work%20as%20migrant%20labourers%20in%20the%20brick%20kilns%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20is%20an%20intra-state%20migrant%20working%20as%20a%20labourer%20at%20construction%20sites.%20Both%20women%20said%20they%20became%20aware%20of%20their%20rights%20under%20MGNREGA%20only%20after%20joining%20the%20JVSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20need%20for%20such%20an%20organisation%20becomes%20apparent%20since%20many%20women%20MGNREGA%20workers%20are%20unaware%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20as%20neither%20the%20village%20mukhiya%20nor%20block%20officers%20deliver%20the%20essential%20information.%20The%20status%20of%20the%20wage%20seekers%20as%20the%20primary%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20Act%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20wage%20seeker%20like%20provision%20of%20cr%C3%A8che%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20first%20aid%20facilities%20on%20worksites%20are%20facilities%20unknown%20to%20them.%20Ranjan%20Kumar%20of%20JVSS%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20women%20and%20educate%20them%20about%20the%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202023-24%2C%20517%20families%20from%20Vaishali%20district%20completed%20100%20days%20of%20work.%20This%20is%20about%200.3%25%20of%20over%20176%2C000%20families%20that%20demanded%20work.%20Across%20Bihar%2C%20this%20number%20was%2023%2C074%20families%20or%200.4%25%20of%20the%205.35%20million%20households%20which%20demanded%20work%2C%20and%200.5%25%20of%20the%204.6%20million%20households%20that%20availed%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%2240f636e4-2fd1-4b13-8ede-5f8facb296d7%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Households%20Completed%20100%20days%20in%20Financial%20Year%202023-24%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approved%20labour%20budget%20for%20the%20scheme%20in%20Bihar%20for%20the%20financial%20year%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnreganarep.nic.in%2Fnetnrega%2FrptCounter.aspx%3FColname%3DApproved%2520Labour%2520Budget%5BIn%2520Lakhs%5D%2520%2520%2520%26Cfin_year%3D2023-2024%26Vc%3D2250%261pfin_year%3D2022-2023%26V1%3D2500%262pfin_year%3D2021-2022%26V2%3D2000%263pfin_year%3D2020-2021%26V3%3D2250%264pfin_year%3D2019-2020%26V4%3D1600%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E225%20million%20person-days%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%2025%20million%20less%20than%20the%20previous%20year.%20Of%20this%2C%20by%20March%2013%2C%20only%2089.6%25%20or%20201.5%20million%20person-days%20of%20work%20were%20completed.%20The%20average%20days%20of%20employment%20provided%20per%20household%20fell%20from%2047.16%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnreganarep.nic.in%2Fnetnrega%2Fall_lvl_details_dashboard_new.aspx%3FFin_Year%3D2023-2024%26Digest%3DWJEEpOm1k0Ptz2KJJGSoqA%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E43.85%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Women%20accounted%20for%2054.29%25%20of%20person%20days%20in%202023-24%2C%20down%20from%2056.39%25%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinki%20Devi%20and%20her%20two%20sisters-in-law%2C%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20Koeri%20community%2C%20residing%20in%20Chhoti%20Dhankar%20village%20of%20Sabour%20block%20in%20Bhagalpur%20district%2C%20possess%20labour%20cards.%20They%20do%20not%20own%20any%20land%2C%20leaving%20them%20to%20rely%20on%20their%20husbands%E2%80%99%20earnings.%20%E2%80%9COur%20husbands%20work%20as%20masons%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devi%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wish%20to%20work%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%2C%20but%20nobody%20has%20ever%20offered%20us%20any%20work%20through%20MGNREGA%2C%20and%20we%20lack%20knowledge%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Though%20they%20are%20job%20card%20holders%2C%20they%20are%20unaware%20of%20the%20procedures%20regarding%20its%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EMen%20migrate%20in%20search%20of%20work%2C%20leaving%20their%20wives%20behind%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%202023%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20released%20by%20Niti%20Aayog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-08%2FIndia-National-Multidimentional-Poverty-Index-2023.pdf%23page%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eranks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Bihar%20at%20the%20top%20in%20the%20list%20of%20states%20suffering%20from%20multidimensional%20poverty.%20The%20men%20in%20the%20state%20migrate%20for%20work%3B%20studies%20suggest%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7659404%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E85%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20migrants%20from%20Bihar%20are%20men.%20The%20women%20they%20leave%20behind%20express%20strong%20interest%20in%20MGNREGS%20work%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20earn%20a%20little%20extra%20while%20still%20leaving%20them%20some%20time%20to%20manage%20household%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWomen%20see%20MGNREGS%20work%20as%20a%20gateway%20into%20the%20wage%20market.%20It%20grants%20them%20greater%20control%20within%20their%20families.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fwcmsp5%2Fgroups%2Fpublic%2F---ed_emp%2Fdocuments%2Fpublication%2Fwcms_613735.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurplus%20money%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20earned%20is%20primarily%20invested%20in%20necessities%20such%20as%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20children%20tend%20to%20discontinue%20education%20and%20engage%20in%20migrant%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnuradha%20Talvar%2C%20a%20veteran%20trade%20union%20activist%2C%20points%20out%20that%20women%20utilise%20the%20money%20they%20earn%20prudently%2C%20and%20do%20not%20indulge%20in%20activities%20such%20as%20alcohol%20and%20gambling.%20Ranjan%20Kumar%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20who%20we%20work%20with%20in%20blocks%20of%20Vaishali%20district%20mostly%20tend%20to%20use%20the%20MGNREGA%20money%20that%20they%20get%20on%20their%20children%20and%20their%20own%20needs%2C%20like%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20poor%2C%20rural%20women%20can%20control%20their%20access%20to%20MGNREGS%20wages%20through%20bank%20accounts%20and%20receive%20adequate%20training%20for%20handling%20it%2C%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20join%20or%20continue%20in%20the%20labour%20workforce%20in%20India%2C%3Cem%3E%20IndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fwomen-more-likely-to-work-if-they-can-control-their-earnings-study%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EUnfavourable%20working%20conditions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPramila%20Devi%2C%20who%20secured%20only%20a%20few%20days%20of%20work%20this%20year%2C%20highlighted%20the%20challenge%20of%20spending%20nearly%2040%20minutes%20walking%20to%20reach%20the%20worksite.%20When%20she%20was%20working%20at%20a%20site%2C%20she%20had%20a%20leg%20injury.%20There%20was%20no%20first%20aid%20kid%20on%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20she%20remembers%20that%20the%20labour%20group%20had%20to%20use%20a%20hand%20pump%20installed%20in%20a%20nearby%20villager%E2%80%99s%20house%20because%20there%20was%20no%20plan%20in%20place%20by%20the%20authorities%20to%20provide%20drinking%20water.%20The%20villager%20was%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20workers%20using%20the%20hand%20pump%20for%20prolonged%20and%20repeated%20periods%2C%20and%20this%20caused%20friction.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20carry%20our%20own%20water%20bottles%20from%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramila%20Devi%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESanju%20Devi%20is%20a%20Mate%20who%20hails%20from%20Muzaffarpur%20district%E2%80%99s%20Dumri%20village%20of%20Mushahari%20block.%20She%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20Gramin%20Vikas%20Manch%2C%20a%20local%20workers%E2%80%99%20organisation.%20Based%20on%20her%20experience%2C%20she%20stresses%20the%20need%20to%20have%20temporary%20restrooms%20at%20the%20worksite%20and%20points%20out%20that%20in%20their%20absence%2C%20women%20workers%20are%20forced%20to%20make%20use%20of%20bushes%20or%20trees%20as%20cover%20while%20they%20relieve%20themselves.%20The%20situation%20becomes%20even%20more%20complicated%20when%20a%20woman%20worker%20is%20menstruating%2C%20Sanju%20Devi%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20was%20no%20cr%C3%A8che%20available%20at%20the%20worksite%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20rules.%20The%20immediate%20elder%20children%20accompany%20their%20mothers%20to%20work%20in%20order%20to%20help%20take%20care%20of%20the%20younger%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERanjan%20Kumar%20from%20JVSS%20works%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20blocks%20of%20a%20total%2016%20blocks%20of%20Vaishali%20district.%20He%20identifies%20Patepur%2C%20Mahua%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viewvillage.in%2Fvillages-of-block%2Fjandaha-2143%5C%22%3EJandaha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viewvillage.in%2Fvillages-of-block%2Fchehrakala-2139%5C%22%3EChehrakala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viewvillage.in%2Fvillages-of-block%2Fgaraul-2141%5C%22%3EGaraul%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bhagwanpur%2C%20and%20Patedi%20Belsar%20as%20the%20blocks%20where%20no%20cr%C3%A8che%20facility%20is%20available%2C%20despite%20the%20organisation%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%20In%20Muzaffarpur%20district%2C%20the%20organisation%20is%20active%20in%20all%2016%20blocks.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20visited%20two%20to%20three%20panchayats%20of%20every%20block%20where%20the%20organisation%20is%20active%2C%20and%20no%20childcare%20provision%20at%20the%20worksite%20was%20to%20be%20found.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESantosh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20local%20activist%20associated%20with%20the%20Gramin%20Vikas%20Manch%20(GVM)%2C%20highlighted%20the%20absence%20of%20cr%C3%A8che%20facilities%20in%20the%20four%20blocks%20%E2%80%93%20Mushahari%2C%20Gaighat%2C%20Kurhani%20and%20Muraul%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Muzaffarpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20%26amp%3B%20Child%20Development%20is%20expanding%20childcare%20services%20via%20anganwadi%20cum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1988976%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECr%C3%A8che%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AWCC)%20as%20part%20of%20Mission%20Shakti%E2%80%99s%20Palna%20sub-component.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20offer%20a%20high-quality%20cr%C3%A8che%20facility%2C%20ensuring%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20children%20aged%20six%20months%20to%20six%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20facilitate%20their%20(women%E2%80%99s)%20entry%20into%20the%20workforce%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20quality%20child%20care%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20announcement%20shows%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20awareness%20of%20childcare%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Talvar%20says.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20a%20scheme%20like%20MGNREGA%20already%20has%20an%20approved%20provision%2C%20it%20should%20be%20implemented.%E2%80%9D%20She%20points%20out%20that%20women%20workers%20often%20talk%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20even%20basic%20toilet%20facilities%20at%20the%20worksite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERenu%20Devi%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20resident%20of%20the%20Patepur%20block%20of%20Nirpur%20Panchayat%2C%20received%2012%20days%20of%20work%20in%20the%20year%202023%E2%80%93first%20for%20five%20days%2C%20and%20then%20for%20a%20week.%20On%20her%20worksite%2C%20every%20employee%20was%20a%20woman.%20She%20has%20a%20three-year-old%20kid%20and%20her%20two%20other%20companions%20were%20also%20mothers%20of%20small%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20asked%20if%20we%20have%20children%20that%20we%20may%20be%20bringing%20to%20the%20worksite%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Her%20three%20children%20are%20three%2C%20five%20and%20eight%20years%20old%2C%20and%20they%20often%20go%20to%20work%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20though%20the%20allotted%20task%20was%20completed%20over%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20she%20has%20still%20not%20gotten%20her%20wages%20for%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20work.%20The%20Gramin%20Rozgar%20Sevak%20avoids%20answering%20her%20questions%20and%20dodges%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EAaega%20aaega%20paisa%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20whenever%20she%20inquires%20about%20employment%20or%20the%20payment%20of%20wages%20for%20work%20previously%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERenu%20Devi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C34%20people%20applied%20for%20a%20labour%20card%20from%20our%20village%20and%20only%2012-14%20of%20them%20received%20the%20cards.%20Others%E2%80%99%20request%20was%20declined%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20lack%20of%20appropriate%20paperwork%20but%20no%20one%20advised%20them%20about%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20being%20neglected%20due%20to%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20dominance%20of%20males.%20The%20MNREGA%20came%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20not%20just%20providing%20work%20but%20work%20on%20equal%20footing%20of%20men%20and%20women.%20However%2C%20while%20there%20are%20complaints%20about%20gender%20disparity%20in%20payment%20at%20several%20places%2C%20the%20bigger%20problem%20is%20the%20failure%20to%20stress%20on%20women-friendly%20work%20and%20delay%20in%20clearing%20wages.%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finspirajournals.com%2Fuploads%2FIssues%2F972590325.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Advanced%20Research%20in%20Commerce%2C%20Management%20%26amp%3B%20Social%20Science%20(IJARCMSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnother%20common%20complaint%20is%20that%20job%20cards%20of%20workers%20are%20often%20deleted%20without%20prior%20intimation.%20The%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F262%2FAU1221.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20parliament%20that%20job%20cards%20are%20deleted%20to%20weed%20out%20fake%2Fincorrect%20cards%2C%20duplicate%20cards%2C%20or%20when%20the%20family%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20work%2C%20has%20permanently%20shifted%20from%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20or%20if%20the%20job%20card%20has%20a%20single%20person%2C%20who%20has%20since%20died.%20Activists%20however%20point%20out%20that%20willing%20workers%20have%20had%20legitimate%20job%20cards%20deleted%2C%20and%20further%20that%20it%20does%20not%20answer%20the%20question%20about%20lack%20of%20prior%20intimation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20MGNREGS%E2%80%99s%20issues%20would%20be%20a%20factor%20influencing%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20vote%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Sinki%20Devi%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20a%20definitive%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20politicians%20who%20come%20seeking%20votes%20in%20the%20village%20hardly%20do%20anything%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20questioning%20the%20political%20will%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20successfully%20implement%20MGNREGS%2C%20Talvar%20also%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20partial%20failure%20of%20labourers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20that%20the%20mismanagement%20of%20the%20scheme%20would%20not%20significantly%20influence%20women%E2%80%99s%20voting%20decisions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Vaishali%20falls%20under%20Ujiarpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20Since%202014%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchanakyya.com%2FParliament-Details%2FUjiarpur%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUjiarpur%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20had%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESchemes%20like%20MGNREGS%20lack%20immediate%20visibility%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20women%20due%20to%20the%20already%20low%20number%20of%20workdays%20and%20delayed%20payment%20in%20numerous%20states%2C%20she%20points%20out.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20rights-based%20framework%20that%20this%20scheme%20has%20is%20not%20perceived%20as%20a%20fundamental%20entitlement%20by%20women%20holding%20labour%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EFew%20women%20in%20supervisory%20roles%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20improve%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20supervisory%20roles%20under%20MGNREGS%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20issued%20a%20policy%20to%20encourage%20%E2%80%98Mahila%20mates%E2%80%99.%20A%20mate%E2%80%99s%20responsibilities%20include%20organising%20groups%20of%20workers%2C%20outlining%20the%20tasks%20that%20are%20needed%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20order%20to%20receive%20the%20minimum%20wage%20(as%20specified%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Schedule%20of%20Rates%E2%80%99)%2C%20and%20keeping%20track%20of%20workers%E2%80%99%20names%20and%20attendance%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20on%20muster%20rolls%20kept%20at%20the%20workplace.%20The%20policy%20leverages%20the%20self-help%20groups%20to%20improve%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20mates%20are%20instructed%20in%20how%20to%20use%20the%20NMMS%20app%20to%20mark%20workers%E2%80%99%20attendance.%20Any%20day%20missed%20results%20in%20loss%20of%20wages%20for%20that%20day.%20The%20primary%20responsibility%20of%20the%20GRS%2C%20which%20is%20an%20appointed%20post%2C%20is%20to%20support%20technical%20personnel%20in%20strengthening%20MGNREGA-related%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPankaj%20Prasun%20is%20a%20Gram%20Rozgaar%20Sevak%20(GRS)%2C%20an%20appointed%20post%20to%20support%20the%20panchayat%20in%20MGNREGS-related%20work.%20A%20mate%20that%20Prasun%20knows%20used%20to%20borrow%20a%20phone%20from%20her%20neighbour%20for%20work%20purposes.%20Block%20officers%20helped%20her%20purchase%20a%20phone%20after%20her%20neighbours%20stopped%20helping.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20forwarded%20this%20concern%20to%20the%20higher%20authority%2C%20but%20maybe%20the%20state%20government%20is%20first%20trying%20to%20check%20the%20success%20of%20the%20mate%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20lack%20of%20mobile%20network%20and%20problems%20in%20registering%20attendance%20is%20affecting%20timely%20wage%20payments%20for%20workers%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fflawed-mgnregs-attendance-app-impacts-workers-pay-in-worlds-largest-rural-jobs-programme-861930%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20block%20to%20which%20Prasun%20has%20been%20appointed%2C%20most%20women%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20role%20of%20a%20mate.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20we%20have%20had%20one%20training%20session%2C%20but%20it%20was%20insufficient%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20all%20the%20knowledge.%20Currently%2C%20all%20we%20have%20to%20do%20is%20assign%20a%20group%20of%20MGNREGA%20workers%20to%20a%20mate%2C%20which%20goes%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20how%20this%20system%20ought%20to%20function.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20mate%20bears%20direct%20responsibility%20for%20verifying%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20muster%20records%20and%20the%20calibre%20of%20labour%20performed.%20They%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20that%20the%20following%20amenities%20are%20provided%20at%20the%20workplace%3A%20a%20place%20to%20live%2C%20a%20medicine%20kit%2C%20and%20workers%20who%20are%20assigned%20to%20provide%20water%20and%20child%20care.%20The%20mate%20is%20also%20tasked%20with%20responding%20to%20crises%2C%20such%20as%20workplace%20mishaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMany%20of%20the%20women%20who%20applied%20to%20be%20a%20mate%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20the%20obligations%20of%20a%20mate%20were.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20told%20to%20fill%20out%20the%20form%20and%20submit%20it%20to%20the%20Jeevika%20office%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20they%20did.%20It%20will%20take%20some%20time%20for%20the%20mates%20to%20completely%20understand%20and%20act%20upon%20the%20purpose%20of%20their%20appointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20area%E2%80%99s%20GRS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERanjan%20Kumar%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20regarding%20block%20officers%20assigning%20their%20acquaintances%20the%20task%20of%20marking%20attendance%20on%20the%20NMMS%20app.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20the%20mate%E2%80%99s%20husband%20comes%20to%20the%20worksite%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20sincere%20in%20marking%20attendance.%20This%20affects%20the%20workers%2C%20because%20without%20attendance%20recorded%20on%20the%20app%2C%20payment%20for%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20labour%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20processed%20even%20if%20the%20person%20has%20worked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20women%20workers%20have%20been%20demanding%20that%20one%20among%20them%20be%20appointed%20the%20mate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20that%20the%20mates%20have%20received%20is%20not%20qualitative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ranjan%20Kumar%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20our%20workers%20in%20the%20union%3B%20therefore%2C%20we%20demand%20their%20appointment.%20The%20government%20should%20be%20more%20efficient%20with%20the%20training%20of%20mates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fhow-mgnregs-continues-to-falter-in-bihar-899476%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20IndiaSpend.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710466248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fhow-mgnregs-continues-to-falter-in-bihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20national%20rural%20jobs%20programme%20in%20Bihar%20and%20found%20allegations%20of%20corruption%2C%20unfavourable%20working%20conditions%2C%20low%20availability%20of%20work%2C%20delayed%20payments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fhow-mgnregs-continues-to-falter-in-bihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20Why%20US%20Wildlife%20Centre%20Staff%20Wears%20Fox%20Mask%20While%20Feeding%20Newborn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEmployees%20at%20Virginia's%20Richmond%20Wildlife%20Center%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20stop%20an%20abandoned%20newborn%20red%20fox%20from%20becoming%20too%20familiar%20with%20humans.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20prevent%20the%20cub%20from%20%26quot%3Bimprinting%26quot%3B%20on%20humans%2C%20the%20employees%20are%20feeding%20the%20red%20fox%20kit%2C%20wearing%20a%20fox%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20made%20headlines%20after%20the%20official%20Facebook%20page%20of%20Richmond%20Wildlife%20Center%20dropped%20a%20video%2C%20showing%20one%20of%20its%20employees%20feeding%20milk%20to%20a%20tiny%20kit.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20the%20employee%20can%20be%20seen%20wearing%20a%20massive%20red%20fox%20head%20mask%2C%20on%20top%20of%20a%20coat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20sure%20of%20the%20hygiene%20factor%20for%20the%20newborn%2C%20the%20employee%20can%20be%20seen%20wearing%20a%20white%20rubber%20glove%2C%20while%20feeding%20milk%C2%A0using%20a%20syringe%20barrel%20connected%20to%20a%20dropper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20was%20shared%20along%20with%20a%20detailed%20note%2C%20wherein%20the%20wildlife%20centre%20revealed%20that%20apart%20from%20wearing%20the%20red%20fox%20head%20mask%2C%20the%20employees%20also%20make%20sure%20to%20%E2%80%9Cminimize%20human%20sounds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20is%20done%20to%20prevent%20the%20newborns%20from%C2%A0imprinting%20on%20humans.%20They%20also%20make%20sure%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20visual%20barriers%20and%20reduce%20multiple%20transfers%20amongst%20different%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20thanks%20to%20everyone%20who%20has%20supported%20the%20Red%20Fox%20Kit.%20She%20is%20progressing%20well.%20It's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20orphans%20that%20are%20raised%20in%20captivity%20do%20not%20become%20imprinted%20upon%20or%20habituated%20to%20humans.%20To%20prevent%20that%2C%20we%20minimize%20human%20sounds%2C%20create%20visual%20barriers%2C%20reduce%20handling%2C%20reduce%20multiple%20transfers%20amongst%20different%20facilities%2C%20and%20wear%20masks%20for%20the%20species.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20able%20to%20locate%20fox%20kits%20of%20the%20same%20age%20and%20weight%20as%20ours%20and%20are%20working%20to%20determine%20what%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20foxes.%20If%20they%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20us%2C%20or%20if%20we%20should%20transfer%20ours%20to%20them.%20Either%20way%2C%20it's%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20this%20Fox%20to%20get%20it%20with%20other%20foxes%20her%20own%20age.%20We%20will%20keep%20you%20posted.%20In%20the%20interim%2C%20enjoy%20this%20video%20of%20Fox%20milk%20time.%20Please%20consider%20sponsoring%20an%20animal%20in%20our%20care%20today.%20Every%20dollar%20counts!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20the%20clip%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FHEALAnimals%252Fvideos%252F804740941687811%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20concludes%20by%20showing%20that%20the%20little%20kit%20is%20given%20a%20red%20fox%20soft-toy%20to%20cuddle%20while%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Ffox-mask-virginia-wildlife-center-kit-fed-newborn-rcna143118%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tiny%20kit%20weighs%20just%2080%20grams%20(2.8%20oz).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20discovered%20by%20Richmond%20SPCA%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20centre%20on%20February%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20initially%2C%20the%20rescuers%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20cat%2C%20but%20soon%20realised%20it%20was%20a%20neonatal%20fox%20kit%2C%20with%20its%20teeth%20yet%20to%20appear.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710465000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fj4fc5vbo_richmond-wildlife-center-fox-facebook_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvirginia-wildlife-centre-staff-pretends-to-be-fox-to-feed-orphaned-newborn-5237163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Employees%20at%20Virginia's%20Richmond%20Wildlife%20Center%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20stop%20an%20abandoned%20newborn%20red%20fox%20from%20becoming%20too%20familiar%20with%20humans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvirginia-wildlife-centre-staff-pretends-to-be-fox-to-feed-orphaned-newborn-5237163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvirginia-wildlife-centre-staff-pretends-to-be-fox-to-feed-orphaned-newborn-5237163%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvirginia-wildlife-centre-staff-pretends-to-be-fox-to-feed-orphaned-newborn-5237163%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yodha%20movie%20review%20and%20release%20LIVE%20Updates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710464858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108507874%2Cimgsize-33178.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyodha-movie-review-box-office-collection-release-live-updates-yodha-sidharth-malhotra-disha-patani-raashi-khanna-yodha-review%2Fliveblog%2F108507874.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%2