%20day%20impact%20wild%20genomes%2C%20Kaebnick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVan%20Eenennaam%20agreed%20that%20the%20genetic%20component%20of%20this%20case%20isn't%20particularly%20worrying.%20Livestock%20cloning%20still%20has%20a%20relatively%20low%20success%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20noted%20that%20bringing%20in%20tissue%20from%20any%20non-native%20species%20could%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-fear-lax-rules-bsl-4-labs-could-lead-pandemic-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiosecurity%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they're%20carrying%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20your%20worst%20nightmare%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20material%20is%20being%20moved%20around%20without%20the%20proper%20clearances%20just%20because%20of%20the%20potential%20threat%20to%20the%20agricultural%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchubarth's%20lawyers%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloned-marco-polo-sheep-lacey-act-sold-dna-offspring-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710453935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ca4f90413ab8e1d64001%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloned-marco-polo-sheep-lacey-act-sold-dna-offspring-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Montana%20man%20was%20charged%20with%20selling%20the%20DNA%20and%20offspring%20of%20a%20cloned%20Marco%20Polo%20sheep%2C%20a%20breed%20known%20for%20its%20horns%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Lacey%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmcgrath%40insider.com%20(Jenny%20McGrath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloned-marco-polo-sheep-lacey-act-sold-dna-offspring-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%