use%20regularly%20don't%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20a%20person's%20overall%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20years%2C%20as%20the%20nutrition%20expert%20has%20dealt%20with%20a%20few%20specific%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20gotten%20just%20a%20tad%20older%20too%2C%20she's%20come%20up%20with%20a%20simple%20regimen%20of%20four%20supplements%20she%20thinks%20may%20help%20her%20age%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20gracefully.%20She's%20well%20aware%20that%20these%20are%20not%20magic%20cure-all%20pills%20or%20silver%20bullets%20for%20her%20longevity.%20But%20her%20research%20has%20shown%20her%20that%20they%20can%20still%20have%20some%20marginal%2C%20positive%20impact%20on%20her%20health%2C%20by%20improving%20some%20of%20the%20nutrient%20issues%20that%20can%20accompany%20aging%2C%20and%20even%20possibly%20staving%20off%20a%20few%20common%20age-related%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20based%20on%20an%20indication%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20looking%20at%20my%20diet%20and%20going%2C%20'I'm%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20to%20that%20level.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20personalized%2C%20data-driven%20supplement%20regimen%20she's%20currently%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVitamin%20D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThomson%2C%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvitamin-d-and-longevity-anti-aging-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20takes%20vitamin%20D.%20Her%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.7326%2FM23-2598%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20showed%20that%20consistent%20vitamin%20D%20supplementation%20among%20thousands%20of%20postmenopausal%20women%20like%20herself%20helped%20prevent%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20colon%20and%20breast%20cancer%20deaths.%20As%20a%20colon%20cancer%20survivor%2C%20she%20takes%20that%20research%20to%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20noticed%20in%20some%20routine%20blood%20tests%20she%20did%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20that%20her%20vitamin%20D%20levels%20had%20dropped%2C%20compared%20to%20where%20they%20were%20when%20she%20was%20younger.%20Taking%20400%20IUs%20a%20day%20seems%20to%20have%20moved%20her%20levels%20back%20up%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20healthy%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalcium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECalcium%20is%20another%20nutrient%20that%20many%20scientists%2C%20including%20Thomson%2C%20have%20shown%20(through%20decades%20of%20long-term%20studies)%20can%20help%20prevent%20deadly%20cancers%20in%20postmenopausal%20women.%20While%20her%20latest%20research%20suggests%20some%20patients%20should%20be%20cautious%20about%20taking%20it%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%20may%20increase%20heart%20disease%20by%20calcifying%20coronary%20arteries%20%E2%80%94%20Thomson%20has%20calculated%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20calcium%20supplementation%20outweigh%20the%20risks%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20history%20of%20colorectal%20cancer%20plus%20her%20diet%20%E2%80%94%20low%20in%20calcium-rich%20animal%20products%20like%20cheese%2C%20yogurt%2C%20and%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20have%20both%20convinced%20her%20this%20supplement%20is%20one%20worth%20taking%2C%20in%20her%20specific%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20take%20calcium%20because%20of%20the%20epidemiological%20evidence%20for%20%5Bcancer%20prevention%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20concerned%20that%20I'm%20not%20getting%20enough%20in%20my%20diet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20probiotic%20capsule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20strong%20course%20of%20antibiotics%20largely%20cleared%20out%20the%20diverse%20and%20important%20garden%20of%20microbes%20living%20inside%20her%20gut%2C%20Thomson%20started%20taking%20a%20daily%20probiotic%20pill.%20She%20suspects%20it%20helps%20keep%20her%20regular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20irritable%20bowel%20afterwards%2C%20and%20I%20just%20stayed%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20helping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMagnesium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMagnesium%20is%20another%20favorite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-supplements-for-longevity-and-anti-aging-expert-recommendations-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupplement%20among%20longevity%20fiends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thomson%20found%20the%20mineral%20to%20be%20a%20useful%20tool%20for%20%26quot%3Bregularity%2C%26quot%3B%20similar%20to%20her%20probiotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20she%20reached%20her%2060s%2C%20she%20also%20started%20taking%20a%20common%20blood%20pressure%20medication%20(a%20diuretic)%20which%20can%20deplete%20magnesium%20stores.%20That%20reinforced%20her%20decision%20to%20keep%20taking%20the%20magnesium%20pills.%20But%20you%20can%20also%20get%20a%20good%20dose%20of%20magnesium%20from%20foods%20like%20spinach%2C%20avocados%2C%20and%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThese%20supplements%20are%20merely%20an%20addition%20to%20her%20plant-heavy%20diet%2C%20where%20she%20gets%20most%20of%20her%20nutrients%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandwich%20with%20vegetables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf4e16f533b039a8846536%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThomson%20says%20most%20of%20her%20diet%20is%20plants.%3Cp%3EGetty%2Falvarez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThomson%20%E2%80%94%20first%20and%20foremost%20%E2%80%94%20prioritizes%20getting%20enough%20of%20all%20of%20the%20above%20nutrients%20(and%20more!)%20through%20her%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20she%20likes%20to%20eat%20tofu%2C%20tempeh%2C%20kefir%2C%20salmon%2C%20nuts%20and%20seeds%2C%20as%20well%20as%20plenty%20of%20vegetables.%20It's%20a%20classic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-longevity-supplements-vs-exercise-and-diet-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20platter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20as%20we%20age%20and%20our%20kidney%20function%20begins%20to%20decline%20and%20our%20liver%20function%20can%20also%20decline%2C%20I%20just%20believe%20in%20plant%20proteins%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20really%20vegan%20or%20vegetarian%20100%25%2C%20but%20I%20really%20push%20a%20lot%20of%20vegetables.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-for-healthy-aging-dietician-vitamin-d-magnesium-calcium-probiotic-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710448650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f357b3857f90b71522bc90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-for-healthy-aging-dietician-vitamin-d-magnesium-calcium-probiotic-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cancer%20prevention%20and%20nutrition%20expert%20has%20picked%20out%20just%20a%20few%20supplements%20to%20enhance%20the%20levels%20of%20key%20nutrients%20she%20gets%20from%20her%20plant-heavy%20diet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-for-healthy-aging-dietician-vitamin-d-magnesium-calcium-probiotic-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian%20President%20Names%20Adviser%20As%20New%20Prime%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20has%20appointed%20Mohammed%20Mustafa%2C%20a%20long-trusted%20adviser%20on%20economic%20affairs%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20official%20Wafa%20news%20agency%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa's%20appointment%20comes%20less%20than%20three%20weeks%20after%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Mohammed%20Shtayyeh%2C%20resigned%2C%20citing%20the%20need%20for%20change%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20of%20October%207%20triggered%20war%20with%20Israel%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2069-year-old%20now%20faces%20the%20task%20of%20forming%20a%20new%20government%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20which%20has%20limited%20powers%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa%2C%20who%20studied%20at%20George%20Washington%20University%20in%20Washington%2C%20is%20an%20independent%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organisation%20--%20dominated%20by%20the%20ruling%20Fatah%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20served%20as%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20for%20economic%20affairs%2C%20held%20a%20board%20seat%20at%20the%20Palestine%20Investment%20Fund%20and%20worked%20in%20several%20senior%20positions%20at%20the%20World%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20advised%20the%20Kuwaiti%20government%20and%20the%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20the%20Public%20Investment%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202007%2C%20control%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20has%20been%20divided%20between%20Abbas's%20Palestinian%20Authority%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa%20was%20involved%20in%20reconstruction%20efforts%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Israel's%202014%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Right-hand%20man'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa's%20appointment%20represents%20an%20attempt%20to%20bolster%20Palestinian%20institutions%20and%20%26quot%3Bclose%20some%20loopholes%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Abbas%20is%20%26quot%3Bunder%20siege%20and%20under%20pressure%26quot%3B%20from%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Palestinian%20analyst%20Abdul%20Majeed%20Sweilem%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa%20would%20likely%20be%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bacceptable%20to%20the%20Americans%20as%20he%20follows%20a%20liberal%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Sweilem%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20Khalil%20Shaheen%2C%20political%20analyst%20and%20writer%2C%20said%20Mustafa's%20closeness%20to%20Abbas%20limits%20prospects%20for%20major%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20man%20(Mustafa)%20remains%20the%20right-hand%20man%20of%20President%20Abbas...%20Abbas%20wants%20to%20say%20that%20he%20supports%20reforms%2C%20but%20they%20remain%20under%20his%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaheen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Gaza%20war%20broke%20out%20after%20Hamas%20operatives%20attacked%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20around%201%2C160%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retaliatory%20Israeli%20military%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2031%2C341%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20war%2C%20violence%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20has%20flared%20to%20levels%20unseen%20in%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20and%20settlers%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20430%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20the%20Gaza%20war%20began%2C%20according%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Ramallah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20other%20powers%20have%20called%20for%20a%20reformed%20Palestinian%20Authority%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20all%20Palestinian%20territories%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Shtayyeh's%20resignation%20in%20late%20February%2C%20Palestinian%20factions%20including%20Hamas%20and%20Fatah%20participated%20in%20talks%20hosted%20by%20Russia%20that%20addressed%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20post-war%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfterward%2C%20the%20factions%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20they%20would%20pursue%20%26quot%3Bunity%20of%20action%26quot%3B%20in%20confronting%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710448440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F970i0q68_palestine-pm_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpalestinian-president-names-adviser-as-new-prime-minister-5240569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20has%20appointed%20Mohammed%20Mustafa%2C%20a%20long-trusted%20adviser%20on%20economic%20affairs%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20official%20Wafa%20news%20agency%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpalestinian-president-names-adviser-as-new-prime-minister-5240569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpalestinian-president-names-adviser-as-new-prime-minister-5240569%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpalestinian-president-names-adviser-as-new-prime-minister-5240569%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uzbek%20woman's%20murder%3A%20What%20investigators%20found%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710447676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108503894%2Cimgsize-22974.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fuzbek-woman-found-dead-in-bengaluru-hotel-hunt-on-for-3-suspects%2Farticleshow%2F108503879.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Za