been%20using%20various%20functionaries%20to%20collect%20personal%20data%20of%20voters%20across%20India.%20This%20ranges%20from%20party%20workers%20involved%20in%20data%20collection%20through%20apps%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.saral.application%26hl%3Den_IE%5C%22%3ESARAL%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20leveraging%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20perceived%20nationalists.%20This%2C%20along%20with%20private%20consultants%20and%20dark%20trade%20of%20data%20brokers%2C%20powers%20the%20data%20collection%20drives%20for%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20personal%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20government%20often%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20which%20use%20it%20for%20electioneering%20purposes.%20Personal%20data%20collected%20by%20political%20parties%20then%20influences%20government%20policy%20after%20elections%2C%20and%20information%20gathered%20by%20parties%20in%20power%20during%20their%20governance%20is%20used%20in%20future%20elections.%20This%20forms%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20electoral%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ECI%20is%20aware%20of%20this%20issue%2C%20it%20has%20not%20taken%20proactive%20measures%20to%20address%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20the%20ECI%20being%20silent%20about%20the%20misuse%20of%20state%20resources%20as%20part%20of%20this%20campaign%2C%20it%20is%20promoting%20it.%20Along%20with%20several%20departments%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20ECI%20and%20its%20chief%20electoral%20officers%20are%20promoting%20this%20campaign%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDemocracy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20banking%20on%20you%20%E2%80%93%20we%20appeal%20to%20all%20Voters%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FElections2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Elections2024%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChunavKaParv%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ChunavKaParv%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDeskKaGarv%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DeskKaGarv%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FECI%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ECI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSVEEP%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SVEEP%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMeraPehlaVoteDeshKeliye%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MeraPehlaVoteDeshKeliye%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FncbobZgOtf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FncbobZgOtf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(%40ECISVEEP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FECISVEEP%2Fstatus%2F1766711426083958913%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20abuse%20of%20state%20machinery%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20but%20is%20seen%20across%20various%20state%20governments.%20In%20case%20of%20political%20campaigns%2C%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20monitor%20them%20and%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20of%20voters.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20elections%2C%20ECI%20has%20always%20ignored%20its%20responsibility%20to%20uphold%20fairness%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20five%20years%20of%20Cambridge%20Analytica%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20consistently%20ignored%20the%20question%20of%20personal%20data%20and%20micro-targeting%20of%20voters.%20As%20India%20goes%20for%20another%20General%20Election%2C%20ECI%20is%20not%20only%20silent%20about%20these%20issues%2C%20it%20is%20openly%20supporting%20the%20abuse%20of%20electoral%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20by%20Parliament%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lack%20of%20enforcement%20of%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Act%20has%20specific%20provisions%20to%20ensure%20data%20is%20not%20used%20in%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20not%20being%20enforced.%20With%20no%20rules%20in%20sight%2C%20the%20ECI%20is%20also%20going%20to%20ignore%20the%20role%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20also%20ignored%20the%20regulation%20of%20the%20social%20media%20and%20online%20advertising%20industry%20by%20allowing%20them%20to%20self-regulate.%20While%20it%20actively%20regulates%20print%20and%20broadcast%20media%20through%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20the%20same%20rules%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20the%20world%20of%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20completely%20obfuscated%20its%20communications%20to%20social%20media%20companies%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20categorising%20them%20as%20third-party%20information%20that%20the%20commission%20cannot%20even%20share%20with%20the%20public.%20Any%20censorship%20of%20social%20media%20content%20ordered%20by%20the%20ECI%20is%20again%20closed%20with%20no%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20increased%20activity%20related%20to%20the%20role%20of%20AI%20and%20DeepFakes%20in%20elections%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20largely%20neglected%20to%20establish%20any%20rules%20or%20guidelines%20regarding%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20flurry%20of%20notices%20and%20advisories%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20related%20to%20AI%20and%20what%20content%20they%20might%20produce%2C%20ECI%20is%20unlikely%20to%20act%20on%20this%20issue%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fintl%2Fen-in%2Fcompany-news%2Foutreach-initiatives%2Fsupporting-the-2024-indian-general-election%2F%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%20by%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20describes%20its%20support%20to%20the%20ECI%20in%20promoting%20election-related%20and%20self-regulation%20activities%20for%20the%20upcoming%20General%20Elections.%20Yet%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20general%20norms%20across%20the%20industry%20should%20ideally%20be%20a%20concern%20for%20the%20ECI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unlikely%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20any%20solutions%20to%20the%20electoral%20challenges%20being%20encountered%20in%20our%20digital%20society.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20intent%20to%20even%20attempt%20to%20address%20these%20problems%20from%20the%20ECI%20shows%20it%20has%20completely%20abdicated%20its%20responsibility%20to%20host%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710423034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14160955%2Fimage-1954.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwith-mera-pehla-vote-desh-ke-liye-campaign-election-commission-openly-boosts-for-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20election%20campaign%20being%20%E2%80%9Claunched%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%20raises%20doubts%20and%20eyebrows.%20Does%20getting%20in%20a%20contestant%20for%20the%20polls%20for%20what%20is%20an%20EC%20activity%2C%20uphold%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98level%20playing%20field%E2%80%99%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwith-mera-pehla-vote-desh-ke-liye-campaign-election-commission-openly-boosts-for-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20the%20ECI%20and%20Union%20Govt%20Passing%20the%20Buck%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Polls%20Post-Delimitation%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10152019%2F27423964742_c550b3b390_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Who%20is%20responsible%20for%20delay%20in%20holding%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%20completion%20of%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%202022%3F%20This%20question%20has%20gained%20significance%20as%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2013%20refuted%20the%20charges%20that%20there%20was%20delay%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20and%20instead%20held%20dissonance%20between%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20and%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20responsible%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20holding%20the%20electoral%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20lays%20blame%20on%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20the%20post-delimitation%20delay%20in%20conducting%20the%20polls%2C%20even%20as%20the%20latter%20has%20been%20passing%20the%20buck%20on%20the%20former%20with%20respect%20to%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20delay%20on%20our%20part%3A%20ECI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20there%20was%20no%20delay%20on%20their%20part%20in%20holding%20the%20electoral%20exercise%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20dissonance%20between%20the%20JandK%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20and%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20completed%20in%202022.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20were%20to%20be%20made%20harmonious%20and%20that%20was%20done%20only%20in%20December%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20referred%20to%20the%20changes%20like%20increase%20in%20assembly%20seats%2C%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20reservation%20of%20two%20seats%20for%20Kashmiri%20migrants%20and%20one%20seat%20for%20refugees%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20were%20to%20be%20incorporated%20in%20the%20Representation%20of%20The%20Peoples%20Act%20and%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwed-high-hopes-of-meeting-the-pm-say-kashmiris-who-werent-allowed-to-enter-the-stadium%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%E2%80%99d%20High%20Hopes%20of%20Meeting%20the%20PM%2C%E2%80%99%20Say%20Kashmiris%20Who%20Weren%E2%80%99t%20Allowed%20to%20Enter%20the%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%20after%20the%20acceptance%20of%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%20(report)%20was%20changed%20in%20December%202023.%20This%20is%20March%2C%202024.%20We%20had%20just%20three%20months.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20no%20delay%20on%20our%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20claim%20raises%20questions%20on%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20took%2017%20months%20to%20amend%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%20to%20incorporate%20the%20changes%20necessitated%20by%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delimitation%20exercise%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1822939%5C%22%3Ecompleted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%205%2C%202022.%20%C2%A0In%20July%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20brought%20a%20bill%20in%20the%20Parliament%20to%20make%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20compatible%20with%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019.%20The%20bill%20was%20cleared%20by%20both%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1983311%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520discussion%252C%2520the%2520Lok%2520Sabha%2Cthe%2520objectives%2520of%2520the%2520bill.%5C%22%3EDecember%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20post-delimitation%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20the%20ECI%20would%20decide%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20polls.%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20has%20also%20made%20similar%20claims%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20suspense%20over%20holding%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20decision%20regarding%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20together%20with%20parliamentary%20elections%20or%20at%20an%20interval%20would%20be%20made%20after%20taking%20into%20account%20inputs%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20security%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20saw%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%202014%20and%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20is%20under%20direct%20control%20of%20Union%20government%20since%20June%2019%2C%202018%20when%20BJP%20withdrew%20support%20to%20the%20Mehbooba%20Mufti-led%20government%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cdeteriorating%E2%80%9D%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20then%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20has%20left%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20Four%20seats%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20also%20vacant%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20due%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20ECI%20to%20hold%20the%20exercise%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDirect%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20assemblies%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20paramount%20features%20of%20representative%20democracy%20in%20India%20cannot%20be%20put%20on%20hold%20until%20statehood%20is%20restored.%20We%20direct%20that%20steps%20shall%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20conduct%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20constituted%20under%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act%20by%2030%20September%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fjudiciary%2Fculmination-of-integration-sc-upholds-abrogation-of-article-370-that-gave-jk-special-status%2F1880334%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20case%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710421200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10152019%2F27423964742_c550b3b390_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-the-eci-and-union-govt-passing-the-buck-on-jammu-and-kashmir-polls-post-delimitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interestingly%2C%20post-delimitation%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20would%20decide%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-the-eci-and-union-govt-passing-the-buck-on-jammu-and-kashmir-polls-post-delimitation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barcelona%20keep%20Dani%20Alves%2C%20jailed%20for%20sexual%20assault%2C%20on%20'legends'%20page%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710420600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x