%20changed%20when%20they%20had%20kids%2C%20the%20travel%20lover%20in%20them%20never%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20cut%20their%20expenses%20on%20travel%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20mini%20home%20on%20wheels.%20They%20bought%20a%20Force%20Traveller%203350%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20caravan%20of%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20they%20find%20time%20between%20their%20jobs%3F%20Deepak%20has%20a%20transferable%20job%2C%20which%20means%20moving%20around%20the%20country%20every%20two%20years.%20He%20makes%20sure%20to%20use%20his%20leaves%20judiciously%20and%20embarks%20on%20a%20trip%20every%20quarter.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20taken%20four%20trips%20in%20their%20van%20%E2%80%94%20Leh%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709958600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-20-1709904937.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20choosing%20the%20right%20vehicle%20to%20planning%20your%20travel%20without%20quitting%20your%20jobs%2C%20this%20list%20of%20tips%20and%20tricks%20from%20seasoned%20caravan%20travellers%20will%20help%20you%20make%20a%20perfect%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344433%2Fvan-life-in-india-tips-caravan-travel-wfh-work-from-home-travelling-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20by%20IIT%20Grads%20Helps%20Indian%20Homes%20Run%20on%20Zero%20Electricity%2C%20Earns%20Rs%20200%20Crore%20in%20Revenues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202020%2C%20entrepreneurs%20Neeraj%20Jain%20and%20Nikhil%20Nahar%20made%20a%20decision%20that%20would%20confound%20most%20entrepreneurs.%20Despite%20running%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20bootstrapped%20and%20profitable%20startup%20centred%20on%20setting%20up%20solar%20power%20installations%20for%20large%20corporations%20since%202015%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20make%2C%20what%20many%20felt%20at%20the%20time%20was%2C%20a%20risky%20pivot%20towards%20the%20(B2C)%20residential%20solar%20segment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20them%20make%20that%20pivot%2C%20Neeraj%20roped%20in%20fellow%20entrepreneur%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT-Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E%20graduate%20Shreya%20Mishra%2C%20who%20had%20prior%20experience%20of%20running%20a%20consumer%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20were%20only%2026%20and%2027%20respectively%20when%20they%20founded%20SolarSquare%20in%202015.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20I%20founded%20Flyrobe%2C%20a%20fashion%20rental%20startup.%20It%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20world%20of%20solar%20energy.%20I%20sold%20my%20startup%20in%202019%2C%20and%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20my%20husband%20Neeraj%20convinced%20me%20to%20join%20SolarSquare.%20He%20was%20an%20engineer%20with%20banking%20experience%20but%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20with%20deep%20meaning%20and%20purpose.%20While%20he%20had%20a%20good%20grasp%20of%20the%20solar%20market%2C%20he%20wanted%20my%20expertise%20in%20building%20consumer%20businesses.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20started%20experimenting%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20more%20B2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shreya%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SolarSquare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20pivot%20because%20the%20industrial%20segment%20is%20very%20different.%20As%20a%20company%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20segment%2C%20SolarSquare%20was%20setting%20up%20massive%20and%20customised%20solar%20power%20installations%20worth%20a%20few%20crores%20for%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20This%20is%20unlike%20the%20residential%20sector%20where%20they%20are%20dealing%20with%20individual%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20took%20a%20very%20bold%20call%20to%20experiment%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20because%20they%20understood%20the%20massive%20business%20opportunity%20it%20offered%20at%20a%20time%20when%20no%20organised%20company%20in%20the%20solar%20energy%20space%20saw%20it.%20They%20saw%20that%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20looked%20like%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future.%20If%20they%20were%20to%20commit%20to%20this%2C%20they%20had%20to%20focus%20all%20their%20energies%20on%20it.%20That%20was%20a%20major%20inflexion%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residential%20solar%20segment%20presented%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future%20because%20average%20Indian%20households%20were%20struggling%20with%20rising%20electricity%20bills%20thanks%20to%20increasing%20tariffs%20and%20regular%20incidences%20of%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%20Rising%20electricity%20costs%20in%20many%20states%20made%20it%20imperative%20for%20consumers%20to%20explore%20alternative%20solutions.%20One%20viable%20solution%20for%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20residential%20societies%20was%20to%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%20power%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Shreya%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20residential%20segment%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%20a%20lot%20of%20standardisation%20in%20solar%20installations%20that%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20scale.%20Imagine%20doing%20tiny%20solar%20installations%20that%20are%20customised%20to%20each%20home!%20It%E2%80%99s%20too%20complex%20a%20process%20for%20a%20B2C%20operation.%20We%20standardised%20everything%20and%20made%20prefabricated%20ready-to-install%20solar%20kits%2C%20which%20get%20installed%20in%20just%20six%20hours.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20underwent%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20innovation%20for%20this%20segment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20three%20and%20half%20years%20later%2C%20SolarSquare%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20residential%20solar%20brand%20in%20India%20with%20a%20consumer%20base%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20over%20100%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311732%2Fmumbai-sustainable-housing-society-saves-water-electricity-navin-chandra-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20societies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20Shreya%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20serendipity%20led%20us%20here.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20operational%20in%2016%20cities%20spread%20across%20eight%20states.%20Over%20two%20rounds%20of%20funding%2C%20we%20have%20raised%20about%20Rs%20130%20crore%20and%20we%E2%80%99ll%20be%20doing%20close%20to%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20revenues%20in%20this%20financial%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20about%2020%25%20of%20SolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20business%20still%20lies%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20solar%20segment%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20pivoted%20close%20to%2080%25%20of%20their%20business%20towards%20the%20residential%20segment.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20have%20also%20doubled%20in%20size%20as%20a%20business%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%2080%25%20of%20our%20business%20is%20in%20the%20residential%20segment%20where%20we%20work%20with%20individual%20homes%20(2BHK%2C%203BHK)%20and%20residential%20societies.%20RWAs%20buy%20solar%20power%20installations%20for%20their%20common%20areas%20like%20lifts%2C%20water%20pumps%2C%20street%20lights%2C%20etc.%20Many%20of%20the%20high-rise%20apartments%20you%20see%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20are%20SolarSquare%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%2