lot%20of%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20awareness%20levels%20were%20very%20nascent%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20first%20mandate%20was%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20on%20the%20back%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceducational%20marketing%20and%20trust.%E2%80%9D%20To%20that%20end%2C%20they%20published%20videos%2C%20content%2C%20and%20blogs%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20influencers%20to%20create%20awareness.%20They%20have%20also%20published%20a%20free%20homeowner%E2%80%99s%20guide%20to%20going%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20installing%20anything%2C%20we%20will%20help%20a%20homeowner%20understand%20why%20solar%20is%20good%20for%20them%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20solar%20installation%20is%20good%20for%20their%20home.%20We%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20first%20educate%20people%20before%20selling%20them%20anything.%20See%2C%20there%20was%20rampant%20mis-selling%20in%20this%20industry.%20Residential%20solar%20is%20a%20fragmented%20and%20unorganised%20market%20involving%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20operators%20who%20do%20this%20as%20a%20side%20business.%20People%20were%20sold%20second%20hand%20or%20rejected%20panels%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20authenticate%20warranty%20or%20quality%20of%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20many%20were%20sold%20solar%20power%20installations%20without%20after-sales%20service.%20If%20you%20are%20buying%20solar%2C%20buying%20the%20right%20after-sales%20service%20is%20very%20important%20because%2C%20without%20it%2C%20your%20investment%20goes%20down%20the%20drain.%20We%20had%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20these%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20SolarSquare%20was%20convincing%20potential%20investors%20that%20their%20decision%20to%20foray%20into%20the%20residential%20segment%20made%20business%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20went%20out%20to%20raise%20funds%2C%20potential%20investors%20thought%20that%20residential%20solar%20is%20a%20small%20market.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20more%20engaged%20in%20fintech%20and%20e-commerce.%20They%20felt%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20very%20brick-and-mortar%20business%20where%20you%20have%20to%20go%20from%20one%20home%20to%20another%2C%20educate%20people%2C%20close%20an%20order%2C%20install%20panels%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20maintain%20them%20for%20years.%20Nobody%20understood%20this%20market%20and%20its%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20June%202022%2C%20Shreya%20claimed%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98%2450%20billion%20opportunity%E2%80%99%20based%20on%20her%20estimates.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20bold%20claim%20back%20then%20given%20how%20international%20market%20research%20and%20advisory%20companies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECustom%20Market%20Insights%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20the%20entire%20Indian%20solar%20energy%20market%20was%20worth%20%2438%20billion%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20back%2C%20I%20probably%20wildly%20underestimated%20the%20market.%20With%20one%20crore%20homes%20potentially%20going%20solar%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20this%20market%20will%20probably%20see%20%2425%20billion.%20In%20a%20decade%2C%20this%20could%20very%20well%20be%20a%20%2475%20billion%20to%20%24100%20billion%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20unique%20time%20in%20history%20where%20you%20can%20create%20a%20consumer%20brand%20in%20energy.%20Otherwise%2C%20energy%20has%20always%20been%20the%20game%20of%20large%20corporations%20and%20Government-owned%20power%20plants.%20Energy%20is%20now%20personal%20and%20private%2C%20and%20we%20can%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289075%2Fisb-grad